's%20official%20data%20suggests%3C%2Fa%3E.%20One%20peek%20under%20the%20hood%20tells%20you%20all%20you%20need%20to%20know.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia's%20car%20industry%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20country's%20most%20important%20sectors%20%E2%80%94%20has%20seen%20a%20total%20collapse%2C%20according%20to%20Yale%20School%20of%20Management%20data%20shared%20with%20Insider.%20Plummeting%20car%20sales%20and%20a%20dramatic%20swing%20in%20the%20type%20of%20cars%20locals%20now%20purchase%20point%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fcurrencies%2Frussia-economy-charts-ukraine-war-oil-trade-europe-sanctions-energy-2023-4%5C%22%3Ebroader%20economic%20woes%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20downward%20spiral%20with%20no%20end%20in%20sight.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20invasion%2C%20about%20100%2C000%20automobiles%20were%20sold%20every%20month%20across%20Russia.%20But%20thanks%20to%20a%20combination%20of%20soaring%20prices%2C%20deteriorating%20consumer%20sentiment%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20supply%2C%20sales%20are%20hovering%20at%20about%20one%20quarter%20of%20pre-war%20levels%2C%20Yale%20researchers%20Jeffrey%20Sonnenfeld%20and%20Steven%20Tian%20told%20Insider%20on%20a%20call%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRussians%20are%20just%20buying%20less%20cars%2C%20period%2C%26quot%3B%20Tian%20said.%20%26quot%3BThat%20speaks%20to%20the%20weakness%20of%20the%20consumer%20in%20Russia.%20This%20is%20as%20close%20to%20a%20proxy%20to%20deteriorating%20consumer%20sentiment%20as%20there%20is%2C%20and%20the%20story%20it%20tells%20is%20profoundly%20distressing.%20Russians%20just%20aren't%20spending%20money.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221202%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Total%20collapse%20in%20Russian%20car%20sales%20amid%20war%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b00ce2c22d1a00194545eb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22849%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussia's%20car%20sector%20has%20seen%20a%20to