%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223648%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMark%20Zuckerberg%20wants%20Threads%20to%20be%20a%20friendly%20space.%3Cp%3EChesnot%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EYou%20can%20already%20buy%20followers%20for%20Instagram's%20Threads.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInsider%20viewed%20several%20websites%20offering%20to%20sell%20followers%20for%20Threads%20accounts.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EInstagram%20has%20long%20battled%20troves%20of%20fake%20followers%2C%20purchases%20likes%2C%20and%20bots.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20are%20now%20a%20week%20into%20the%20existence%20of%20Threads%20and%20there's%20already%20a%20robust%20menu%20of%20followers%20you%20can%20buy%20on%20the%20internet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20offer%20of%20%247.50%20for%20100%20followers%2C%20to%20%241%2C900%20for%2050%2C000%20followers%20on%20Instagram's%20Threads%20app%2C%20paid%20engagement%20services%20and%20bot%20farms%20are%20pouncing%20on%20a%20new%20market%2C%20according%20to%20a%20review%20of%20a%20handful%20of%20sites%20by%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInstagram%20has%20long%20battled%20bots%20and%20juiced%20engagement%20on%20the%20app.%20The%20platform%20has%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finstagram-deleting-fake-likes-follows-third-party-apps-2018-11%5C%22%3Edeleting%20fake%20followers%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20likes%20for%20years%2C%20and%20Instagram%20even%20has%20a%20section%20about%20this%20behavior%20in%20its%20community%20guidelines.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHelp%20us%20stay%20spam-free%20by%20not%20artificially%20collecting%20likes%2C%20followers%2C%20or%20shares%2C%20posting%20repetitive%20comments%20or%20content%2C%20or%20repeatedly%20contacting%20people%20for%20commercial%20purposes%20without%20their%20consent%2C%26quot%3B%20Instagram's%20community%20guidelines%20page%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222616%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Screengrab%20of%20different%20prices%20for%20fake%20followers%20on%20Threads%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64af124b94be880019f3ad73%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFameSavy%20is%20one%20of%20many%20services%20offering%20packages%20for%20followers%20on%20Threads.%3Cp%3EScreengrab%2FFameSavy%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20influencer-marketing%20platform%20HypeAuditor%2C%20on%20average%2C%20about%2013.8%25%20of%20influencers'%20Instagram%20followers%20are%20categorized%20as%20%26quot%3Bsuspicious%26quot%3B%20accounts.%20HypeAuditor%20defines%20suspicious%20accounts%20as%20any%20Instagram%20page%20that%20appear%20to%20be%20bots%20or%20%26quot%3Buse%20specific%20services%20for%20likes%2C%20comments%2C%20and%20followers%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20told%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20follower%20count%20metric%20still%20holds%20some%20weight%2C%20especially%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20securing%20and%20negotiating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-get-instagram-sponsorship-small-accounts%5C%22%3Ebrand%20deals%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20an%20influencer%2C%20it%20isn't%20so%20clear%20how%20important%20follower%20count%20will%20be%20for%20Threads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20start%2C%20followers%20aren't%20as%20prominently%20showcased%20on%20Threads%20as%20they%20are%20on%20Instagram%20(or%20Twitter%2C%20for%20that%20matter).%20The%20number%20itself%20is%20at%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20bio%20and%20appears%20muted%20when%20stacked%20with%20other%20vibrant%20buttons%20and%20text.%20And%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20algorithms%2C%20ranking%20on%20Threads%20is%20more%20dependent%20on%20what%20content%20someone%20interacts%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20do%20rank%20posts%20lightly%20and%20show%20recommendations%20(posts%20from%20accounts%20you%20don't%20follow)%20in%20feed%2C%20which%20is%20particularly%20important%20for%20a%20new%20app%20before%20people%20follow%20enough%20accounts%2C%26quot%3B%20head%20of%20Instagram%20Adam%20Mosseri%20wrote%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.threads.net%2Ft%2FCuT2p98N7Rn%5C%22%3Ea%20recent%20Thread%20reply%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBuying%20an%20influx%20of%20spam%20followers%20on%20Threads%20could%20very%20well%20do%20nothing%20to%20help%20an%20account%20grow%20or%20find%20success%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-many-followers-on-instagram-to-get-paid%5C%22%3Eas%20a%20creator%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20Insider's%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-can-already-buy-fake-followers-instagram-threads-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689262805000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64a62d906075be0019c2c6c8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-can-already-buy-fake-followers-instagram-threads-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22That%20didn't%20take%20long.%20Insider%20spotted%20several%20websites%20offering%20deals%20for%20inflated%20follower%20metrics%20on%20Threads.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbradley%40insider.com%20(Sydney%20Bradley)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A22%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finfluencers-can-already-buy-fake-followers-instagram-threads-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22You'll%20now%20be%20able%20to%20get%20birth%20control%20without%20a%20prescription%20%E2%80%94%20but%20it%20won't%20hit%20store%20shelves%20until%202024%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223555%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20box%20of%20OPill%2C%20the%20first%20over-the-counter%20birth%20control%20pill%20in%20a%20teal%20package%20with%20blue%2C%20lavender%20and%20pink%20detailing%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b004a99751e3001929f140%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222666%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20FDA%20approved%20an%20over-the-counter%20birth%20control%20pill.%3Cp%3EPerrigo%2FAssociated%20Press%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20FDA%20approved%20the%20first%20over-the-counter%20birth%20control%20pill.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EStarting%20in%202024%2C%20Perrgio's%20once-a-day%20OPill%20will%20be%20available%20without%20a%20prescription.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EAdvocates%20pushed%20for%20expanding%20birth%20control%20access%2C%20especially%20with%20more%20restrictions%20on%20abortion.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EU.S.%20officials%20have%20approved%20the%20first%20over-the-counter%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fbirth-control%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirth%20control%20pill%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20will%20let%20American%20women%20and%20girls%20buy%20contraceptive%20medication%20from%20a%20retail%20store%20without%20a%20prescription.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThe%20Food%20and%20Drug%20Administration%20said%20Thursday%20it%20cleared%20Perrigo's%20once-a-day%20Opill%20to%20be%20sold%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20making%20it%20the%20first%20such%20medication%20to%20be%20moved%20out%20from%20behind%20the%20pharmacy%20counter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20won't%20start%20shipping%20the%20pill%20until%20early%20next%20year%2C%20and%20there%20will%20be%20no%20age%20restrictions%20on%20sales.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EHormone-based%20pills%20have%20long%20been%20the%20most%20common%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fguides%2Fhealth%2Freproductive-health%2Fhow-long-does-it-take-for-birth-control-to-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirth%20control%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%20US%2C%20used%20by%20tens%20of%20millions%20of%20women%20since%20the%201960s.%20Until%20now%2C%20all%20of%20them%20required%20a%20prescription.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EMedical%20societies%20and%20women's%20health%20groups%20have%20pushed%20for%20wider%20access%2C%20noting%20that%20an%20estimated%2045%25%20of%20the%206%20million%20annual%20pregnancies%20in%20the%20US%20are%20unintended.%20Teens%20and%20girls%2C%20women%20of%20color%20and%20those%20with%20low%20incomes%20report%20greater%20hurdles%20in%20getting%20prescriptions%20and%20picking%20them%20up.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIreland-based%20Perrigo%20did%20not%20announce%20a%20price.%20Over-the-counter%20medicines%20are%20generally%20much%20cheaper%20than%20prescriptions%2C%20but%20they%20aren't%20covered%20by%20insurance.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPerrigo%20submitted%20years%20of%20research%20to%20the%20FDA%20to%20show%20that%20women%20could%20understand%20and%20follow%20instructions%20for%20using%20the%20pill.%20Thursday's%20approval%20came%20despite%20some%20concerns%20by%20FDA%20scientists%20about%20the%20company's%20results%2C%20including%20whether%20women%20with%20certain%20underlying%20medical%20conditions%20would%20understand%20they%20shouldn't%20take%20the%20drug.%3Cbr%3EFDA's%20action%20only%20applies%20to%20Opill%20%E2%80%94%20not%20other%20birth-control%20pills.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt's%20in%20an%20older%20class%20of%20contraceptives%2C%20sometimes%20called%20mini%20pills%2C%20that%20contain%20a%20single%20synthetic%20hormone%20and%20generally%20carry%20fewer%20side%20effects%20than%20more%20popular%20combination%20hormone%20pills.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EBut%20women's%20health%20advocates%20hope%20the%20decision%20will%20pave%20the%20way%20for%20more%20over-the-counter%20birth%20control%20options%20and%2C%20eventually%2C%20for%20abortion%20pills%20to%20do%20the%20same.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThat%20said%2C%20FDA's%20decision%20has%20no%20relation%20to%20the%20ongoing%20court%20battles%20over%20the%20abortion%20pill%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fthe-abortion-pill-what-to-know-about-self-managed-abortions-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emifepristone%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20studies%20in%20Perrigo's%20FDA%20application%20began%20years%20before%20the%20Supreme%20Court's%20reversal%20of%20Roe%20v.%20Wade%2C%20which%20has%20upended%20abortion%20access%20across%20the%20US.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ENewer%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-does-birth-control-work%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebirth%20control%20pills%3C%2Fa%3E%20typically%20combine%20two%20hormones%2C%20estrogen%20and%20progestin%2C%20which%20can%20help%20make%20periods%20lighter%20and%20more%20regular.%20But%20their%20use%20carries%20a%20heightened%20risk%20of%20blood%20clots%20and%20they%20shouldn't%20be%20used%20by%20women%20at%20risk%20for%20heart%20problems%2C%20such%20as%20those%20who%20smoke%20and%20are%20over%2035.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EOpill%20has%20only%20progestin%2C%20which%20prevents%20pregnancy%20by%20blocking%20sperm%20from%20reaching%20the%20cervix.%20It%20must%20be%20taken%20around%20the%20same%20time%20daily%20to%20be%20most%20effective.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIn%20its%20internal%20review%20published%20in%20May%2C%20the%20FDA%20noted%20that%20some%20women%20in%20Perrigo's%20study%20had%20trouble%20understanding%20the%20drug's%20labeling%20information.%20In%20particular%2C%20the%20instructions%20warn%20that%20women%20with%20a%20history%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.insider.com%2Fbirth-control-breast-cancer-risk-study-decide-progestogen-combined-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebreast%20cancer%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20not%20take%20the%20pill%20because%20it%20could%20spur%20tumor%20growth.%20And%20women%20who%20have%20unusual%20vaginal%20bleeding%20are%20instructed%20to%20talk%20to%20a%20doctor%20first%20because%20it%20could%20indicate%20a%20medical%20problem.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EPerrigo%20executives%20said%20the%20company%20will%20spend%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20year%20manufacturing%20the%20pill%20and%20its%20packaging%20so%20it%20can%20be%20available%20in%20stores%20nationwide%20and%20online%20by%20early%20next%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbirth-control-pill-now-available-without-prescription-contraceptives-opill-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689262772000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b0047a9751e3001929f12e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbirth-control-pill-now-available-without-prescription-contraceptives-opill-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20FDA%20approved%20the%20first%20birth%20control%20pill%20available%20without%20a%20prescription%2C%20expanding%20access%20to%20contraceptives.%20It%20will%20hit%20shelves%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Associated%20Press)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbirth-control-pill-now-available-without-prescription-contraceptives-opill-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%5C%22At%206%20I%20Was%20Molested...%5C%22%3A%20Star%20England%20Footballer%20Dele%20Alli%20Reveals%20Abuse%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Dele%20Alli%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F98427-dele-alli-playerprofile%5C%22%3EDele%20Alli%3C%2Fa%3E%20revealed%20on%20Thursday%20that%20he%20has%20recently%20come%20out%20of%20rehab%20for%20a%20sleeping%20pill%20addiction%20after%20struggling%20to%20deal%20with%20the%20trauma%20of%20suffering%20sexual%20abuse%20as%20a%20child.%20The%20Everton%20midfielder%2C%20who%20was%20once%20one%20of%20English%20football's%20brightest%20talents%2C%20told%20Gary%20Neville's%20%26quot%3BThe%20Overlap%26quot%3B%20podcast%20about%20how%20he%20was%20also%20dealing%20drugs%20by%20age%20eight%20before%20his%20life%20was%20changed%20by%20being%20adopted%20by%20a%20new%20family%20as%20a%2012-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlli%2C%2027%2C%20shot%20to%20fame%20under%20Mauricio%20Pochettino%20at%20Tottenham%20and%20was%20a%20key%20part%20of%20the%20England%20side%20that%20reached%20the%202018%20World%20Cup%20semi-finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20career%20on%20the%20field%20has%20been%20in%20decline%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20he%20fell%20out%20of%20favour%20at%20Spurs%20before%20struggling%20to%20make%20an%20impact%20at%20Everton%20or%20on%20loan%20at%20Besiktas%20last%20season.%20However%2C%20he%20explained%20how%20those%20struggles%20are%20rooted%20in%20a%20series%20of%20childhood%20traumas%20that%20he%20tried%20to%20block%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20six%20I%20was%20molested%20by%20my%20mum's%20friend%2C%20who%20was%20at%20the%20house%20a%20lot.%20My%20mum%20was%20an%20alcoholic%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Alli.%20%26quot%3BThen%20I%20was%20sent%20to%20Africa%20(to%20his%20father)%20to%20learn%20discipline%20and%20then%20I%20was%20sent%20back.%20(At)%20seven%20I%20started%20smoking%2C%20eight%20I%20started%20dealing%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAn%20older%20person%20told%20me%20that%20they%20wouldn't%20stop%20a%20kid%20on%20a%20bike%2C%20so%20I%20rode%20around%20with%20my%20football%2C%20and%20then%20underneath%20I'd%20have%20the%20drugs%2C%20that%20was%20eight.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEleven%2C%20I%20was%20hung%20off%20a%20bridge%20by%20a%20guy%20from%20the%20next%20estate%2C%20a%20man.%20Twelve%2C%20I%20was%20adopted...%20I%20was%20adopted%20by%20an%20amazing%20family%20like%20I%20said%2C%20I%20couldn't%20have%20asked%20for%20better%20people%20to%20do%20what%20they'd%20done%20for%20me.%20If%20God%20created%20people%2C%20it%20was%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESleeping%20pill%20problem%20widespread%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlli%20added%20that%20he%20hopes%20by%20speaking%20out%20he%20can%20help%20others%20that%20have%20suffered%20similar%20abuse.%20Prince%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22William%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F96765-william-carvalho-playerprofile%5C%22%3EWilliam%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Alli's%20former%20Tottenham%20teammate%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Harry%20Kane%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ffootball%2Fplayers%2F95920-harry-kane-playerprofile%5C%22%3EHarry%20Kane%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20among%20those%20to%20pay%20tribute%20to%20his%20bravery%20in%20coming%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBrave%20and%20inspirational%20%40dele_official%2C%26quot%3B%20tweeted%20the%20Prince%20of%20Wales%2C%20who%20is%20an%20ambassador%20for%20mental%20health%20charities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDiscussing%20mental%20health%20is%20not%20a%20sign%20of%20weakness.%20Let's%20keep%20the%20conversation%20going.%20We're%20all%20with%20you%20and%20we%20wish%20you%20the%20very%20best.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKane%20and%20Alli%20struck%20up%20a%20prolific%20partnership%20in%20the%20early%20days%20of%20their%20career%20together%20at%20Spurs.%20%26quot%3BProud%20of%20%40dele_official%20for%20speaking%20out%20and%20sharing%20his%20experience%20to%20try%20and%20help%20others%2C%26quot%3B%20tweeted%20the%20England%20captain.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlli%20he%20said%20a%20six-week%20spell%20in%20rehab%20in%20the%20United%20States%20has%20helped%20rekindle%20his%20passion%20to%20get%20his%20football%20career%20back%20on%20track.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoing%20into%20rehab%20is%20definitely%20scary%20but%20I%20could%20never%20have%20imagined%20how%20much%20I%20would%20get%20from%20it%20and%20how%20much%20it%20would%20help%20me%20mentally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20was%20in%20a%20bad%20place.%20A%20lot%20happened%20when%20I%20was%20younger%20that%20I%20could%20never%20understand.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20warned%20that%20the%20dangers%20of%20sleeping%20pill%20addiction%20are%20widespread%20in