20stock%20to%20own%20thanks%20to%20its%20growing%20exposure%20to%20anime%20content%20via%20its%20Crunchyroll%20streaming%20service%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Wednesday%20note%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fstocks%2Fgs-stock%5C%22%3EGoldman%20Sachs.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20upgraded%20Sony%20to%20%26quot%3BBuy%26quot%3B%20from%20%26quot%3BNeutral%26quot%3B%20and%20set%20a%20price%20target%20of%20%C2%A516%2C000%20for%20the%20Tokyo-listed%20shares%2C%20suggesting%20potential%20upside%20of%20nearly%2030%25%20from%20current%20levels.%20For%20Sony's%20ADR%20shares%2C%20it%20would%20suggest%20a%20price%20target%20of%20about%20%24115.%20Goldman%20also%20added%20Sony%20to%20its%20conviction%20list%2C%20which%20highlights%20the%20bank's%20top%20stock%20ideas.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESony%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftech%2Fwhat-is-crunchyroll%5C%22%3Eacquired%20Crunchyroll%20from%20AT%26amp%3BT%20in%202021%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Goldman%20expects%20the%20anime-focused%20streaming%20service%20to%20help%20boost%20the%20company's%20operating%20profits%20as%20well%20as%20increase%20the%20demand%20for%20anime%20content%20around%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20past%2C%20overseas%20consumers%20had%20no%20means%20of%20accessing%20a%20broad%20range%20of%20Japanese%20anime%2C%20but%20the%20emergence%20of%20streaming%20services...%20provides%20access%20to%20anime%20content%20for%20any%20consumer%20with%20a%20smartphone%2C%20PC%2C%20tablet%20or%20other%20device%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20explained.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20bank%20said%20Crunchyroll%20is%20making%20a%20significant%20contribution%20to%20anime's%20growth%20in%20overseas%20markets%2C%20and%20that%20by%202036%20they%20will%20account%20for%2080%25%20of%20Japanese%20anime%20sales.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECrunchyroll%20currently%20has%20just%20over%2010%20million%20paying%20subscribers%20and%20generated%20an%20estimated%20%241%20billion%20in%20annual%20revenue.%20Goldman%20expects%20that%20figure%20to%20double%20to%2020%20million%20subscribers%20by%202027.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCrunchyroll%20in%20unique%20position%20as%20a%20dedicated%20anime%20distribution%20platform...%20Crunchyroll%20is%20now%20positioned%20as%20the%20most%20appealing%20platform%20for%20Japanese%20anime%20fans%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20content%20volume%20and%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20quality%20of%20content%20is%20a%20sticking%20point%20for%20many%20anime%20fans%2C%20and%20Goldman%20said%20Sony%20can%20play%20to%20that%20strength%20by%20acquiring%20and%20developing%20exclusive%20anime%20content%20that%20drives%20fans%20to%20sign%20up%20for%20the%20service.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Sony%20succeeds%20in%20growing%20its%20Crunchyroll%20subscriber%20base%2C%20it%20could%20improve%20earnings%20stability%2C%20as%20they%20will%20be%20less%20driven%20by%20the%20staggered%20release%20of%20blockbuster%20games%20on%20its%20Playstation%205%20console.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20also%20expect%20Crunchyroll%20to%20make%20stable%20earnings%20contributions%2C%20as%20its%20business%20centers%20on%20video%20distribution%20and%20revenues%20comprising%20a%20large%20part%20of%20monthly%20subscription%20fees.%20Accordingly%2C%20we%20expect%20Sony's%20future%20earnings%20to%20be%20less%20dependent%20on%20the%20single-year%20game%20and%20entertainment%20content%20pipeline%20than%20before%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsony-stock-price-anime-content-exposure-crunchyroll-streaming-goldman-sachs-2023-7%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689261802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64b00b7fc22d1a001945458f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsony-stock-price-anime-content-exposure-crunchyroll-streaming-goldman-sachs-2023-7%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BCrunchyroll%20is%20now%20positioned%20as%20the%20most%20appealing%20platform%20for%20Japanese%20anime%20fans%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20content%20volume%20and%20quality%2C%26quot%3B%20Goldman%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mfox%40businessinsider.com%20(Matthew%20Fox)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fsony-stock-price-anime-content-exposure-crunchyroll-streaming-goldman-sachs-2023-7%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20What%20Transplanting%20A%20Tree%20Amid%20Gunfight%20Says%20About%20Manipur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EJune%2011%2C%202023%20will%20be%20remembered%20as%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20day%20for%20Mud%20village%2C%20which%20lies%20in%20the%20foothills%20between%20Manipur's%20Kangpokpi%2C%20Ukhrul%20and%20Imphal%20East%20districts.%20It%20will%20remain%20a%20remarkable%20day%20in%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20small%20team%20comprising%20a%20filmmaker%2C%20a%20producer%2C%20farmers%2C%20an%20army%20Captain%20and%20some%20soldiers%2C%20who%20successfully%20transplanted%20a%205.5-feet-tall%2C%20fruit-bearing%20hog%20plum%20tree%2C%20locally%20known%20as%20%26quot%3B%3Cem%3Eheining%3C%2Fem%3E%26quot%3B%2C%20amid%20the%20intermittent%20ethnic%20clashes%20in%20Manipur%20since%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMud%20is%20a%201.25%20hectare-large%20concept%20village%20near%20Manipur's%20%26quot%3Bliving%20museum%26quot%3B%20at%20Sekta%2C%2023%20km%20from%20state%20capital%20Imphal.%20Tree%20and%20bamboo%20plantations%20are%20prioritised%20activities%20here%20since%202020.%20The%20place%20serves%20as%20a%20landscaping%20exercise%20to%20run%20an%20environmentally%20friendly%20village%20and%20also%20serves%20as%20a%20community%20interactive%20centre%2C%20a%20family%20outdoor%20activity%20spot%2C%20a%20space%20for%20specialised%20residential%20training%20programmes%20and%20a%20meditation%20centre.%20All%20these%20are%20essentially%20for%20self-exploration%20and%20understanding%20nature.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20digging%20a%20water-harvesting%20pond%20the%20size%20of%20half%20a%20football%20field%20in%20April%20this%20year%2C%20the%20focus%20has%20so%20far%20been%20on%20planting%20fruit-bearing%20and%20indigenous%20trees%20and%20local%20bamboo%20species.%20Apart%20from%20a%20long%20list%20of%20prized%20possession%20-%20olive%2C%20guava%2C%20gooseberry%2C%20mango%2C%20jackfruit%2C%20wild%20apple%2C%20papaya%2C%20pear%2C%20star%20fruit%20and%20Arjun%20tree%20(Arjuna%20Myrobalan)%20-%20Mud%20village%20is%20now%20home%20to%20the%205.5-feet-tall%20hog%20plum%20tree.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMuch%20like%20picturesque%20Manipur%2C%20the%20charm%20of%20Mud%20village%20is%20the%20surrounding%20hill%20ranges%20offering%20outdoor%20adventure%20activities%20like%20trekking%20and%20camping.%20Another%20attraction%20is%20the%20remnant%20of%20the%20Second%20World%20War%20atop%20Chanung%20hill%2C%20just%20above%20the%20village.%20Trenches%20and%20bunkers%20built%20by%20the%20Japanese%20Army%20on%20the%20ridges%20of%20Chanung%20during%20their%20siege%20of%20Imphal%20still%20exist%2C%20more%20or%20less%20in%20the%20shape%20and%20size%20they%20were%20built%20in%201944.%20The%20allied%20forces%20used%20to%20call%20these%20fortifications%20%26quot%3Bpimples%26quot%3B.%20It%20is%20recorded%20in%20the%20war%20history%20that%20the%20Japanese%20siege%20of%20Imphal%20failed%20as%20the%20allied%20forces%20kept%20supply%20lines%20intact%20with%20air%20drops.%20This%20strategy%20helped%20the%20Allies%20win%20the%20Imphal%20and%20Kohima%20battles%20and%20made%20the%20Japanese%20surrender.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20why%20all%20this%20history%20now%2C%20and%20what%20is%20so%20extraordinary%20about%20a%20hog%20plum%20tree%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%224pivepag%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2F4pivepag_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20turbulent%20times%20that%20Manipur%20has%20been%20living%20in%20since%20May%203%20is%20extraordinary.%20The%20consequences%20and%20the%20after-effects%20of%20the%20'peace%20rally'%20called%20by%20the%20All%20Tribal%20Students'%20Union%20of%20Manipur%20(ATSUM)%20are%20unprecedented.%20The%20provocation%20for%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20that%20drew%20the%20fault%20line%20between%20the%20Kukis%20and%20the%20Meiteis%20is%20astounding.%20The%20nature%20of%20the%20communal%20violence%20seen%20in%20the%20hills%20and%20the%20valley%20is%20horrendous.%20The%20way%20social%20media%20is%20manipulated%20to%20push%20narratives%20is%20distasteful.%20The%20way%20most%20in%20the%20national%20media%20and%20celebrity%20talk-show%20hosts%20buying%20the%20narratives%20without%20any%20fact-checking%20is%20even%20more%20indigestible.%20Hence%2C%20the%20extraordinariness%20of%20the%20ethnic%20violence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unfathomable%20violence%20of%20burning%20down%20houses%2C%20looting%20properties%20and%20targeting%20people%20and%20villages%20have%20become%20the%20very%20basis%20for%20a%20sweeping%20narrative%20that%20separation%20is%20the%20only%20solution.%20This%20call%20came%20from%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%2C%20the%20two%20hill%20districts%20dominated%20by%20the%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribe.%20They%20have%20held%20on%20to%20the%20narrative%20that%20their%20community%20is%20under%20attack%20and%20they%20have%20been%20chased%20away%20from%20the%20valley%2C%20just%20as%20the%20Meiteis%20who%20were%20living%20in%20the%20hill%20districts%20of%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Tengnoupal%20have%20been%20evacuated%20and%20have%20taken%20shelter%20in%20the%20valley.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20tribes%20want%20a%20separate%20political%20administration%20from%20the%20valley%2C%20or%20specifically%2C%20the%20Meiteis.%20There%20is%20little%20scope%20for%20a%20reconciliation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESignificantly%2C%20this%20narrative%20emerged%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20violence%20broke%20out.%20For%20a%20state%20that%20has%20seen%20much%20ethnic%20violence%20-%20the%20Kuki-Naga%20bloodbath%20in%20the%20early%201990s%2C%20the%20Kuki-Paite%20clash%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20and%20the%20Meitei-Muslim%20clash%20-%20Manipur%20has%20never%20had%20a%20narrative%20about%20separate%20administration%20or%20autonomy.%20In%20the%20past%2C%20reconciliation%20worked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EQuite%20naturally%2C%20for%20a%20multi-ethnic%20civilization%20living%20in%20harmony%20for%20a%20long%20time%2C%20with%20written%20records%20dating%20back%20to%202000%20years%20since%2033%20AD%2C%20meddling%20with%20its%20territorial%20and%20political%20integrity%20seemed%20non-negotiable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22agv4goho%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-06%2Fagv4goho_manipur-violence-ani_625x300_12_June_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20chronologically%20seen%2C%20trouble%20started%20in%20Churachandpur%20with%20the%20burning%20of%20a%20forest%20department%20office%20before%20the%20'tribal%20solidarity%20peace%20rally'%20began%2C%20in%20which%20insurgents%20in%20camouflage%20battle%20dress%20armed%20with%20AK-56%20rifles%20were%20clearly%20seen%20participating.%20Subsequently%2C%20reports%20of%20attacks%20on%20homes%20and%20shops%20of%20unarmed%20Meiteis%20in%20Bishnupur%20district%20bordering%20Churachandpur%20and%20in%20the%20international%20border%20town%20of%20Moreh%20started%20coming.%20SOS%20calls%20by%20the%20trapped%20Meiteis%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20after%20which%20even%20the%20suspension%20of%20internet%20services%20from%20May%203%20evening%20could%20not%20prevent%20the%20retaliatory%20attacks%20by%20the%20Meiteis%20in%20the%20valley.%20The%20Chin-Kuki-Zo%20people%20who%20made%20Imphal%20their%20home%20had%20to%20flee%20for%20safety%20to%20Churachandpur%20and%20Kangpokpi%20as%20they%20had%20become%20the%20targets%20of%20the%20Meitei%20rage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20initial%20violence%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20over%2040%2C000%20central%20forces%2C%20the%20dark%20smoke%20gradually%20subsided%20in%20Imphal%20valley%2C%20Churachandpur%2C%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Tengnoupal%20districts.%20However%2C%20sporadic%20gunfights%20continued%20in%20the%20foothills%20where%20the%20valley%20ends%20and%20the%20hills%20start%2C%20especially%20in%20areas%20bordering%20Kuki-Chin-Zo%20dominated%20areas.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVisuals%20of%20gunfights%20between%20people%20of%20the%20two%20communities%20armed%20with%20weapons%20looted%20from%20the%20Manipur%20Police%20armoury%2C%20licenced%20rifles%2C%20country-made%20weapons%20and%20those%20imported%20from%20Myanmar%20came%20out%20from%20Sugnu%20and%20Serou%20between%20Kakching%20in%20the%20valley%20and%20Chandel%20in%20the%20hills%2C%20Phayeng-Senjam%20Chirang%20between%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Imphal%20West%2C%20and%20Khamenlok%2C%20which%20borders%20Kangpokpi%20and%20Imphal%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20returning%20to%20the%20story%20of%20the%20hog%20plum%20tree%2C%20Mud%20village%20is%205%20km%20away%20from%20the%20two%20troubled%20areas%20of%20Chanung%20and%20Khamenlok.%20Other%20than%20taking%20the%20inter-village%20roads%2C%20both%20areas%20can%20be%20reached%20by%20hiking%20up%20the%20Tombakhong%20hill%20range%20to%20reach%20Chanung%20and%20then%20trek%20further%20up%20south%20to%20reach%20Khamenlok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20two%20areas%20are%20vulnerable%20to%20attacks%20and%20counterattacks%20between%20the%20warring%20factions.%20Villagers%20here%20are%20compelled%20to%20keep%20watch%20with%20their%20licenced%20guns%2C%20and%20in%20some%20cases%20are%20supported%20by%20well-armed%20volunteers%20on%20both%20sides.%20There%20is%20a%20palpating%20sense%20of%20perpetual%20threat%20and%20the%20first%20to%20launch%20the%20offensive%20naturally%20gets%20the%20better%20of%20the%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22ocnoegqo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Focnoegqo_manipur-violence-_625x300_05_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDays%20before%20the%20ethnic%20violence%20began%2C%20a%20residential%20school%20built%20to%20international%20standards%20was%20inaugurated%20at%20Chanung.%20This%20school%20was%20the%20target%20of%20arson%20by%20well-armed%20Kukis%2C%20who%20climbed%20down%20the%20hill%20ranges%20from%20Khamenlok.%20Fortunately%2C%20the%20prompt%20response%20of%20the%20Central%20Reserve%20Police%20Force%20(CRPF)%20foiled%20the%20attack%20in%20May-end.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20incident%20exposed%20the%20vulnerability%20of%20Chanung%2C%20Loushangkhong%20and%20Sekta%20areas%20to%20Kuki%20attacks.%20Villagers%20in%20Chanung%20and%20Loushangkhong%20took%20turns%20to%20keep%20watch%20and%20built%20makeshift%20bunkers.%20Weary%20of%20keeping%20a%20constant%20eye%20on%20possible%20attacks%2C%20the%20villagers%20are%20said%20to%20have%20discussed%20securing%20the%20whole%20area%20in%20Chanung%20and%20Khamenlok%20to%20stop%20them%20from%20being%20used%20as%20launchpads%20by%20armed%20Kukis%20to%20strike%20at%20Meitei%20villages%20in%20Imphal%20East.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESensing%20the%20volatile%20situation%2C%20the%20Indian%20Army%20also%20set%20up%20makeshift%20outposts%20on%20top%20of%20Langthabi%20hill%2C%20directly%20looking%20down%20at%20Mud%20village.%20The%20army's%20presence%20in%20the%20bunkers%20uphill%20made%20the%20situation%20more%20tense%20as%20the%20villagers%20alleged%20the%20central%20forces%20failed%20to%20stop%20the%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20this%20atmosphere%2C%20the%20developers%20of%20Mud%20village%20had%20to%20transplant%20the%20healthy%20hog%20plum%20tree%2C%20gifted%20to%20them%20by%20a%20local%20elder.%20The%20tree%20had%20grown%20bigger%20for%20the%20spot%20it%20was%20planted%20on.%20Normally%2C%20the%20developers%20would%20have%20taken%20the%20tree%20on%20the%20dirt%20road%20and%20transplanted%20it.%20But%20the%20situation%20did%20not%20allow%20it%20this%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20developers%20then%20contacted%20the%20Commanding%20Officer%20(CO)%20of%20the%20area%20and%20told%20him%20of%20their%20plan%20to%20transplant%20the%20hog%20plum%20tree.%20The%20CO%20courteously%20gave%20a%20patient%20hearing%20and%20told%20the%20team%20to%20wait.%20Fifteen%20minutes%20later%2C%20an%20army%20Captain%20called%20and%20asked%20about%20the%20plan%20again.%20Then%20he%20drove%20down%20in%20an%20SUV%20and%20met%20the%20team%20at%20a%20bridge%20that%20connected%20the%20two%20villages.%20After%20a%20brief%20conversation%2C%20the%20army%20Captain%20came%20with%20the%20team.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22hd3f02qo%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fhd3f02qo_manipur-violence-_625x300_05_May_23.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20how%20the%20hog%20plum%20tree%20was%20transplanted%20at%20Mud%20village%20on%20June%2011%2C%20with%20two%20Indian%20Army%20personnel%20participating.%20This%20was%20an%20extraordinary%20moment%20-%20people%20transplanting%20a%20tree%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20an%20ethnic%20clash.%20In%20the%20next%20three%20days%2C%20unfortunately%2C%20the%20areas%20between%20Mud%20village%20and%20Khamenlok%20saw%20the%20biggest%20single-day%20fatalities%20and%20maximum%20burning%20down%20of%20homes%20since%20violence%20started%20on%20May%203.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20June%2012%2C%20the%20Kuki%20villages%20of%20Khopibung%2C%20Khamenlok%2C%20Chullouphai%20and%20Aigejang%20were%20destroyed%20by%20armed%20Meitei%20village%20volunteers.%20Some%20of%20them%20decided%20to%20spend%20the%20night%20at%20Aigejang%20church.%20In%20the%20counterattack%2C%20well-armed%20Kuki%20forces%20reportedly%20fired%20rocket-propelled%20grenades%20at%20the%20church%2C%20killing%20the%20nine%20Meiteis%2C%20leaving%20four%20missing%20and%20nine%20others%20injured.%20The%20next%20day%2C%20Meitei%20volunteers%20went%20on%20to%20burn%20down%20nine%20more%20Kuki%20villages%20in%20Khamenlok.%20On%20June%2028%2C%20reports%20of%20landmines%20around%20Khamenlok%20came%2C%20after%20which%20the%20army%20and%20state%20forces%20went%20on%20a%20mission%20to%20defuse%20the%20mines.%20The%20combine%20forces%2C%20however%2C%20detected%20numerous%20well-armed%20Kuki%20insurgents%20dressed%20in%20black.%20Such%20was%20the%20scale%20of%20violence%20seen%20at%20Khamenlok.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20countermeasures%20of%20the%20combined%20forces%20have%20stepped%20up.%20These%20measures%20have%20succeeded%20in%20recovering%20looted%20guns%2C%20ammunition%20and%20bombs.%20Altogether%2C%201%2C100%20guns%2C%2013%2C700%20bullets%20and%20250%20bombs%20have%20been%20recovered%20so%20far.%20The%20combined%20forces%20also%20destroyed%20a%20number%20of%20bunkers%20used%20by%20both%20communities%20to%20launch%20attacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExtraordinarily%2C%20the%20hog%20plum%20tree%20has%20grown%20well%2C%20sprouting%20stems%20and%20even%20leaves%20from%20its%20new%2C%20serene%20abode%2C%20surrounded%20by%20the%20enchanting%20hill%20ranges%20that%20have%20seen%20the%20worst%20ever%20bloodbath%20in%20Manipur%2C%20the%20jewelled%20land.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ESunzu%20Bachaspatimayum%20is%20an%20independent%20journalist%20and%20an%20award-winning%20filmmaker%20based%20in%20Manipur.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689261660000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fec1496o8_manipur-violence_625x300_28_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fwhat-transplanting-a-tree-amid-gunfight-tells-about-manipur-4204500%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22June%2011%2C%202023%20will%20be%20remembered%20as%20the%20most%20extraordinary%20day%20for%20M