ns%2C%20are%20set%20to%20rise%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20the%20country's%20public%20sector%20wage%20increase%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20British%20Indian%20leader%2C%20who%20was%20under%20pressure%20to%20accept%20the%20recommendation%20of%20an%20independent%20review%20of%20pay%20for%20teachers%2C%20police%2C%20junior%20doctors%20and%20other%20public%20sector%20workers%2C%20confirmed%20a%20hike%20between%205%20and%207%20per%20cent%20across%20the%20board.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20he%20stressed%20that%20this%20would%20not%20be%20met%20with%20higher%20government%20borrowing%20for%20fear%20of%20further%20stoking%20high%20inflation%20and%20therefore%20the%20costs%20would%20need%20to%20be%20found%20elsewhere.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20we're%20going%20to%20prioritise%20paying%20public%20sector%20workers%20more%2C%20that%20money%20has%20to%20come%20from%20somewhere%20else%20because%20I'm%20not%20prepared%20to%20put%20up%20people's%20taxes%20and%20I%20don't%20think%20it%20would%20be%20responsible%20or%20right%20to%20borrow%20more%20because%20that%20would%20just%20make%20inflation%20worse%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Sunak%20told%20reporters%20at%20a%20Downing%20Street%20press%20conference.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20what%20we%20have%20done%20are%20two%20things%20to%20find%20this%20money.%20The%20first%20is%2C%20we%20are%20going%20to%20increase%20the%20charges%20that%20we%20have%20for%20migrants%20who%20are%20coming%20to%20this%20country%20when%20they%20apply%20for%20visas%20and%20indeed%20something%20called%20the%20Immigration%20Health%20Surcharge%20(IHS)%2C%20which%20is%20the%20levy%20that%20they%20pay%20to%20access%20the%20NHS%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20of%20those%20fees%20are%20going%20to%20go%20up%20and%20that%20will%20raise%20over%20GBP%201%20billion%2C%20so%20across%20the%20board%20visa%20application%20fees%20are%20going%20to%20go%20up%20significantly%20and%20similarly%20for%20the%20IHS%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Sunak%20reiterated%20this%20was%20%26quot%3Bentirely%20right%26quot%3B%20as%20these%20fees%20have%20not%20been%20increased%20recently%20and%20the%20government%20believes%20it%20is%20appropriate%20given%20that%20the%20costs%20have%20risen%20since%20the%20last%20hike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20second%20action%20to%20meet%20the%20country's%20higher%20wage%20bill%20is%20about%20asking%20government%20departments%20to%20%26quot%3Breprioritise%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20insisted%20this%20would%20not%20mean%20cuts%20to%20jobs%20and%20services%20but%20a%20re-focusing%20on%20different%20priorities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20IHS%2C%20which%20applies%20to%20long-term%20migrants%20to%20the%20UK%20including%20a%20discounted%20rate%20for%20students%2C%20starts%20from%20around%20GBP%20470%20for%20a%20year%20and%20rises%20to%20thousands%20of%20pounds%20for%20multiple-year%20visa%20applications.%3Cbr%3E%5CnThe%20full%20details%20of%20which%20categories%20of%20visas%20will%20face%20hikes%20and%20when%20the%20new%20higher%20rates%20come%20into%20force%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20laid%20out%20by%20the%20UK%20Home%20Office%20in%20the%20coming%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sunak-led%20Conservative%20Party%20government%20has%20been%20under%20intense%20pressure%20with%20disputes%20over%20the%20public%20sector%20pay%2C%20leading%20to%20a%20series%20of%20strikes%20over%20the%20past%20year%20hitting%20schools%20and%20hospitals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20junior%20doctors%20in%20England%20began%20yet%20another%20five-day%20strike%20on%20Thursday%20after%20their%20demands%20for%20a%2035%20per%20cent%20pay%20hike%20were%20rejected.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20wage%20announcement%2C%20Mr%20Sunak%20warned%20that%20his%20offer%20was%20%26quot%3Bfinal%26quot%3B%20and%20further%20industrial%20action%20would%20not%20change%20that%20decision.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20will%20be%20no%20more%20talks%20on%20pay.%20We%20will%20not%20negotiate%20again%20on%20this%20year's%20settlements%20and%20no%20amount%20of%20strikes%20will%20change%20our%20decision.%20Instead%2C%20the%20settlement%20we've%20reached%20today%20gives%20us%20a%20fair%20way%20to%20end%20the%20strikes.%20A%20fair%20deal%20for%20workers%20and%20a%20fair%20deal%20for%20the%20British%20taxpayer%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20welcomed%20teachers'%20unions%20expressing%20their%20backing%2C%20saying%20the%20government's%20offer%20will%20allow%20teachers%20and%20school%20leaders%20to%20call%20off%20their%20strike%20action%20and%20resume%20normal%20relations.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689261300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fhblgr79k_london-generic_625x300_05_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-visa-fees-health-surcharge-to-go-up-significantly-rishi-sunak-4204874%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Fees%20and%20health%20surcharge%20paid%20towards%20the%20UK's%20National%20Health%20Service%20by%20visa%20applicants%20from%20around%20the%20world%2C%20including%20Indians%2C%20are%20set%20to%20rise%20%26quot%3Bsignificantly%26quot%3B%20to%20meet%20the%20country's%20public%20sector%20wage%20increase%2C%20Prime%20Minister%20Rishi%20Sunak%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-visa-fees-health-surcharge-to-go-up-significantly-rishi-sunak-4204874%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-visa-fees-health-surcharge-to-go-up-significantly-rishi-sunak-4204874%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-visa-fees-health-surcharge-to-go-up-significantly-rishi-sunak-4204874%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Assam%20Backs%20Civil%20Code%2C%20Wants%20To%20Ban%20Polygamy%20Immediately%3A%20Chief%20Minister%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Assam%20government%20has%20already%20conveyed%20to%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20that%20it%20is%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20and%20wants%20to%20ban%20polygamy%20in%20the%20state%20immediately%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UCC%20is%20a%20matter%20which%20will%20be%20decided%20by%20Parliament%2C%20but%20the%20state%20can%20also%20take%20a%20call%20on%20it%20with%20the%20assent%20of%20the%20President%2C%20CM%20Sarma%20said%20at%20the%20sidelines%20of%20a%20programme%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''UCC%20involves%20various%20issues%20and%20the%20Law%20Commission%20as%20well%20as%20the%20Parliamentary%20Committee%20is%20looking%20into%20it.%20The%20Assam%20government%20has%20already%20conveyed%20that%20it%20is%20in%20its%20support%2C''%20the%20chief%20minister%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPending%20the%20decision%20on%20the%20UCC%2C%20''we%20want%20to%20take%20one%20of%20its%20segments%20-%20polygamy%20-%20and%20ban%20it%20immediately.%20We%20are%20planning%20to%20introduce%20a%20Bill%20to%20ban%20it%20in%20the%20next%20assembly%20session%20in%20September%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChief%20Minister%20Sarma%2C%20also%20a%20senior%20BJP%20leader%2C%20said%20if%20the%20state%20government%20is%20unable%20to%20table%20the%20Bill%20for%20some%20reason%2C%20it%20will%20be%20done%20in%20the%20January%20session.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20meantime%2C%20however%2C%20if%20the%20UCC%20is%20implemented%2C%20we%20do%20not%20have%20to%20take%20this%20action%20as%20it%20will%20be%20merged%20with%20it%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20the%20Congress'%20opposition%20to%20the%20UCC%2C%20the%20chief%20minister%20wondered%20if%20a%20leader%20of%20that%20party%20has%20a%20daughter%2C%20''will%20the%20person%20marry%20her%20off%20to%20somebody%20with%20two%20wives''.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20problem%20is%20that%20Congress%20leaders%20do%20not%20realise%20the%20pain%20of%20Muslim%20women.%20They%20take%20their%20votes%20but%20they%20do%20not%20want%20to%20give%20back%20anything%20to%20them''%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20wants%20the%20votes%20of%20both%20Muslim%20men%20and%20women%20but%20they%20want%20to%20serve%20only%20the%20men%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Even%20Nabi%20(The%20Prophet)%20did%20not%20support%20polygamy%20as%20he%20had%20said%20that%20all%20Muslims%20should%20ideally%20have%20one%20wife.%20These%20are%20the%20essential%20points%20of%20Islam.%20The%20Congress%20should%20not%20support%20polygamy%20and%20stand%20with%20Muslim%20women%2C%20even%20if%20they%20lose%20some%20votes%2C''%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20had%20opposed%20the%20abolition%20of%20triple%20talaq%20and%20now%20the%20UCC%2C%20so%20in%20a%20way%20the%20party%20is%20''waging%20a%20war%20against%20Muslim%20women''%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''When%20they%20(Muslim%20women)%20emancipate%20themselves%20from%20the%20influence%20of%20the%20male%2C%20they%20will%20punish%20the%20Congress''%2C%20Mr%20Sarma%20claimed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERegarding%20opposition%20by%20AIUDF's%20Badruddin%20Ajmal%2C%20CM%20Sarma%20asserted%20that%20he%20is%20the%20voice%20of%20Muslim%20men%20and%20not%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20are%20always%20interacting%20with%20Muslim%20women%20and%20they%20say%20that%20they%20have%20a%20problem%20as%20they%20cannot%20speak%20out%20openly.%20They%20also%20tell%20us%20that%20Allah%20will%20always%20bless%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C''%20the%20BJP%20leader%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20UCC%20refers%20to%20a%20common%20set%20of%20laws%20on%20marriage%2C%20divorce%20and%20inheritance%20that%20would%20be%20applicable%20to%20all%20Indian%20citizens%20irrespective%20of%20religion%2C%20tribe%20or%20other%20local%20customs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Law%20Commission%20had%20on%20June%2014%20initiated%20a%20fresh%20consultation%20process%20on%20UCC%20by%20seeking%20views%20from%20stakeholders%2C%20including%20public%20and%20recognised%20religious%20organisations%2C%20on%20the%20politically%20sensitive%20issue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EImplementation%20of%20the%20UCC%20has%20been%20part%20of%20the%20BJP's%20election%20manifesto.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689261060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-05%2Fsc0983t4_himanta-sarma-1200_625x300_06_May_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-supports-uniform-civil-code-wants-to-ban-polygamy-immediately-chief-minister-himanta-sarma-4204384%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Assam%20government%20has%20already%20conveyed%20to%20the%20authorities%20concerned%20that%20it%20is%20in%20support%20of%20the%20Uniform%20Civil%20Code%20(UCC)%20and%20wants%20to%20ban%20polygamy%20in%20the%20state%20immediately%2C%20Chief%20Minister%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20said%20today.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-supports-uniform-civil-code-wants-to-ban-polygamy-immediately-chief-minister-himanta-sarma-4204384%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-supports-uniform-civil-code-wants-to-ban-polygamy-immediately-chief-minister-himanta-sarma-4204384%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fassam-supports-uniform-civil-code-wants-to-ban-polygamy-immediately-chief-minister-himanta-sa