aden-Guest%20over%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaden-Guest%20had%20called%20his%20friend%20a%20%26quot%3Bmiserable%20blob%26quot%3B%20as%20dinner%20took%20a%20turn%20when%20climate%20change%20came%20up.%20Dechert%2C%20who%20reportedly%20screamed%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20climate%20hoax!%26quot%3B%20Not%20satisfied%2C%20Dechert%20then%20resorted%20to%20farting%20to%20underline%20his%20point%2C%20presumably%20exacerbating%20the%20greenhouse%20effect%20in%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKennedy%20Jr.%2C%20an%20environmentalist%20who%20has%20pivoted%20to%20dismissing%20vaccine%20science%2C%20was%20described%20as%20maintaining%20a%20%26quot%3Bsteady%20composure%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20crisis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESure%2C%20his%20uncle%2C%20President%20John%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20faced%20down%20the%20Cuban%20missile%20crisis.%20And%20his%20father%2C%20Robert%20F.%20Kennedy%2C%20was%20in%20the%20thick%20of%20the%20federal%20response%20to%20defending%20civil%20rights%20protestors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20not%20everyone%20can%20choose%20their%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaden-Guest%20said%20he%20just%20simply%20couldn't%20believe%20his%20decades-long%20friend%20would%20dismiss%20climate%20change.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDoug%20said%20it%20was%20a%20hoax%20and%20scam%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20The%20Post.%20%26quot%3BA%20scam%20for%20who%3F%20Who%20is%20benefiting%3F%20That's%20not%20a%20political%20thing%2C%20it's%20a%20human%20existence%20thing.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20The%20Post%20called%20Dechert%20after%20the%20affair%2C%20he%20was%20apologetic%20for%20his%20rhetorical%20tactic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20apologize%20for%20using%20my%20flatulence%20as%20a%20medium%20of%20public%20commentary%20in%20your%20presence.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20then%20asked%20to%20be%20referred%20to%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bgallivanting%20boulevardier%26quot%3B%20or%20a%20%26quot%3Bbeer-fueled%20sex%20rocket.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20only%2C%20Dechert%20was%20in%2