89%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Era%20Of%20Equality%3A%20ICC%20Announces%20Equal%20Prize%20Money%20For%20Men's%2C%20Women's%20Events%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20men's%20and%20women's%20teams%20at%20ICC%20events%20while%20also%20making%20changes%20to%20the%20over-rate%20sanctions%20in%20Test%20cricket.%20%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20was%20taken%20at%20the%20ICC%20Annual%20Conference%20in%20Durban%2C%20South%20Africa%20and%20ensures%20the%20ICC%20Board%20fulfilled%20its%20commitment%20to%20reaching%20prize%20money%20equity%20by%202030%20well%20ahead%20of%20schedule%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETeams%20will%20now%20receive%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20the%20equivalent%20finishing%20position%20at%20comparable%20events%20as%20well%20as%20the%20same%20amount%20for%20winning%20a%20match%20at%20those%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20from%20the%20next%20cycle%20will%20award%20the%20same%20prize%20money%20to%20men's%20and%20women's%20champions%20and%20runners-up%20teams%20at%20its%20global%20events.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20significant%20moment%20in%20the%20history%20of%20our%20sport%20and%20I%20am%20delighted%20that%20men's%20and%20women's%20cricketers%20competing%20at%20ICC%20global%20events%20will%20now%20be%20rewarded%20equally.%20Since%202017%20we%20have%20increased%20prize%20money%20at%20women's%20events%20every%20year%20with%20a%20clear%20focus%20on%20reaching%20equal%20prize%20money%20and%20from%20here%20on%20in%2C%20winning%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20will%20carry%20the%20same%20prize%20money%20as%20winning%20the%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%20and%20the%20same%20for%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20U19s%20too%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20Chair%20Greg%20Barclay%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20ICC.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%26amp%3B%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20am%20thrilled%20to%20announce%20that%20a%20major%20step%20towards%20gender%20parity%20%26amp%3B%20inclusivity%20has%20been%20undertaken.%20The%20prize%20money%20at%20all%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FICC%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%40ICC%3C%2Fa%3E%20events%20will%20be%20same%20for%20men%20%26amp%3B%20women.%20Together%20we%20grow....%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Jay%20Shah%20(%40JayShah)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJayShah%2Fstatus%2F1679494208569364480%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCricket%20is%20genuinely%20a%20sport%20for%20all%20and%20this%20decision%20from%20the%20ICC%20Board%20reinforces%20that%20and%20enables%20us%20to%20celebrate%20and%20value%20every%20single%20player's%20contribution%20to%20the%20game%20equally%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ICC%20Board%20also%20confirmed%20the%20largest%20ever%20investment%20into%20the%20sport%20after%20the%20distribution%20model%20for%20the%20next%20four%20years%20was%20agreed%20upon.%20Every%20ICC%20Member%20will%20receive%20significantly%20enhanced%20funding%20with%20a%20strategic%20investment%20fund%20ring-fenced%20to%20drive%20global%20growth%20initiatives%20in%20line%20with%20the%20ICC%20Global%20Growth%20Strategy.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20champions%20and%20runners-up%20of%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20T20%20World%20Cup%202020%20and%202023%20won%20USD%201%20million%20and%20USD%20500%2C000%2C%20respectively%2C%20a%20fivefold%20increase%20over%20the%20sum%20awarded%20in%202018%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20statement%20further%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20prize%20money%20for%20the%20ICC%20Women's%20Cricket%20World%20Cup%202022%20has%20been%20increased%20to%20USD%203.5%20million%2C%20up%20from%20USD%202%20million%20for%20winning%20the%202017%20edition%20in%20England%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20aded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chief%20Executives'%20Committee%20has%20approved%20changes%20to%20Test%20cricket's%20over-rate%20fines%20in%20order%20to%20achieve%20a%20balance%20between%20the%20necessity%20of%20preserving%20over-rates%20and%20providing%20equitable%20compensation%20for%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnder%20the%20new%20rules%2C%20which%20will%20take%20effect%20at%20the%20start%20of%20the%20current%20World%20Test%20Championship%20cycle%2C%20players%20will%20be%20fined%205%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20match%20fee%20for%20each%20over%20that%20falls%20short%2C%20with%20a%20maximum%20penalty%20of%2050%20per%20cent.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20if%20a%20side%20is%20bowled%20out%20before%20reaching%20the%2080-over%20mark%20and%20the%20new%20ball%20has%20not%20yet%20been%20delivered%2C%20there%20will%20be%20no%20over-rate%20penalty%20enforced%2C%20regardless%20of%20any%20prospective%20delays.%20This%20amendment%20replaces%20the%20previous%20requirement%20of%2060%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20ICC%20World%20Test%20Championship%20has%20injected%20renewed%20energy%20into%20Test%20cricket%20giving%20it%20compelling%20context%2C%26quot%3B%20ICC%20Men's%20Cricket%20Committee%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Sourav%20Ganguly%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F197-sourav-ganguly-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESourav%20Ganguly%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20in%20an%20official%20statement%20released%20by%20ICC.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20last%20edition%20we%20only%20had%2012%20draws%20in%2069%20matches%2C%20and%20we%20want%20to%20ensure%20that%20trend%20continues%20whilst%20we're%20giving%20fans%20the%20best%20value%20for%20money%20and%20keeping%20over-rates%20up.%20The%20Men's%20Cricket%20Committee%20felt%20strongly%20that%20over-rate%20penalties%20in%20the%20form%20of%20WTC%20points%20deductions%20should%20remain%20but%20recommended%20that%20players%20should%20not%20have%20100%20per%20cent%20of%20their%20match%20fee%20at%20risk.%20We%20believe%20this%20provides%20a%20balance%20between%20maintaining%20over-rates%20and%20ensuring%20we%20are%20not%20deterring%20players%20from%20playing%20Test%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689259020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-02%2Fb5l2qsl8_smriti-mandhana-afp_625x300_22_February_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20(ICC)%20on%20Thursday%20announced%20equal%20prize%20money%20for%20men's%20and%20women's%20teams%20at%20ICC%20events%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fera-of-equality-icc-announces-equal-prize-money-for-mens-womens-team-events-4204707%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bob%20Iger%20says%20Disney's%20TV%20and%20cable%20business%20'may%20not%20be%20core'%20and%20leaves%20the%20door%20open%20to%20a%20sale%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22bob%20iger%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5d829dd72e22af151e1459d3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22683%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBob%20Iger%3Cp%3EValerie%20Macron%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EDisney's%20Bob%20Iger%20said%20the%20company's%20TV%20and%20cable%20businesses%20may%20not%20be%20core.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20plans%20to%20be%C2%A0%26quot%3Bexpansive%26quot%3B%20about%20how%20Disney%20treats%20those%20as%20it%20responds%20to%20the%20shift%20to%20streaming.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIger%2C%20who%20just%20extended%20his%20contract%20for%202%20more%20years%2C%20also%20weighed%20in%20on%20Hulu%20and%20ESPN%20plans.%C2%A0%20%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EDisney's%20no-growth%20TV%20and%20cable%20businesses%20%26quot%3Bmay%20not%20be%20core%26quot%3B%20to%20the%20company%20and%20it%20will%20be%20%26quot%3Bexpansive%26quot%3B%20about%20how%20it%20treats%20them%2C%20CEO%20Bob%20Iger%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIger's%20comments%20came%20during%20an%20expansive%20interview%20on%20CNBC%20Thursday%2C%20a%20day%20after%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdisney-ceo-bob-iger-extends-contract-legacy-succession-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecompany%20extended%20his%20time%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20the%20company%20for%20two%20more%20years%2C%20through%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20Disney%20would%20sell%20those%20properties%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0%3Cspan%3Ewhich%20include%20ABC%20and%20cable%20networks%20like%20FX%20and%20National%20Geographic%20%E2%80%94%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Iger%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BWe're%20going%20to%20look%20expansively%20at%20opportunities%20there.%20They%20may%20not%20be%20core%20to%20Disney.%20The%20business%20model%20underpinning%20those%20businesses%20is%20definitely%20broken.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIger%20addressed%20those%20and%20the%20myriad%20challenges%20at%20the%20company%20as%20it%20manages%20the%20shift%20to%20streaming%20that's%20upended%20the%20media%20industry%2C%20as%20well%20as%20%26quot%3Bsome%20self-inflicted%26quot%3B%20issues.%20Iger%20said%20while%20he's%20accomplished%20a%20lot%2C%20he%20and%20the%20board%20agreed%20there%20was%20much%20more%20to%20do%2C%20and%20that