the%20border%20dispute%2C%20showed%20the%20first%20signs%20of%20a%20slowdown%20in%20years%20falling%20by%200.9%20per%20cent%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year.China's%20exports%20to%20India%20in%20the%20first%20half%20of%20this%20year%20totalled%20%2456.53%20billion%20compared%20to%20%2457.51%20billion%20last%20year%20registering%20a%20decline%20of%200.9%20per%20cent%2C%20according%20to%20the%20data%20released%20by%20Chinese%20customs%20on%20Thursday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22PTI%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A15%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fbusiness%2Findia-business%2Findia-china-trade-shows-first-signs-of-slowdown-in-years%2Farticleshow%2F101733165.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Amendment%20To%20GST%20Act%20On%20Online%20Gaming%20In%20Parliament%20Monsoon%20Session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ERevenue%20Secretary%20Sanjay%20Malhotra%20today%20said%20the%20central%20government%20will%20bring%20clarificatory%20amendments%20to%20the%20GST%20Act%20in%20the%20monsoon%20session%20of%20Parliament%20to%20implement%20GST%20Council's%20decision%20of%20imposing%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20online%20gaming%2C%20casino%20and%20horse%20racing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20monsoon%20session%20will%20begin%20on%20July%2020%20and%20end%20on%20August%2011%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20will%20be%20our%20effort%20to%20draft%20the%20law%20and%20introduce%20it%20in%20Parliament%20and%20get%20it%20passed%20in%20the%20monsoon%20session%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Press%20Trust%20of%20India%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20implementation%20takes%20effect%20only%20when%20state%20legislatures%20have%20also%20passed%20amendments%20in%20state%20GST%20laws%2C%20he%20said%2C%20adding%2C%20that%20it%20will%20take%20some%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20clarificatory%20amendment.%20It%20has%20been%20our%20view%20that%20online%20games%20for%20stakes%20depend%20on%20outcomes...whether%20game%20of%20skill%20or%20game%20of%20chance.%20The%20Council%20has%20only%20reiterated%20and%20confirmed%20that%20view%20that%20these%20games%20are%20taxable%20at%2028%20per%20cent%20on%20the%20full%20face%20value%20or%20the%20payment%20which%20is%20made%20to%20the%20online%20gaming%20platform%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20in%20that%20sense%20it%20is%20not%20retrospective%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20online%20gaming%20companies%2C%20however%2C%20have%20been%20paying%20tax%20at%20lower%20rates%20on%20Gross%20Gaming%20Revenue%20(GGR)%20which%20works%20out%20to%20be%20less%20than%205%20per%20cent%20which%20is%20applicable%20on%20food%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Goods%20and%20Services%20Tax%20(GST)%20Council%20in%20its%20meeting%20on%20Tuesday%20decided%20to%20impose%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20tax%20on%20the%20turnover%20of%20online%20gaming%20companies%2C%20horse%20racing%20and%20casinos.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20rate%20was%20decided%20based%20on%20the%20recommendation%20of%20a%20group%20of%20ministers%20that%20looked%20at%20taxing%20casinos%2C%20horse%20racing%20and%20online%20gaming.%20The%20issue%20before%20the%20GoM%20(group%20of%20ministers)%20was%20whether%20to%20impose%20a%2028%20per%20cent%20GST%20on%20the%20face%20value%20of%20bets%2C%20or%20gross%20gaming%20revenue%2C%20or%20just%20on%20platform%20fees.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20GST%20Council%20decided%20to%20impose%20tax%20on%20the%20entire%20value.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20tax%20on%20online%20gaming%20companies%20would%20be%20imposed%20without%20making%20any%20differentiation%20based%20on%20whether%20the%20games%20required%20skill%20or%20were%20based%20on%20chance.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689255060000%2C%22visu