%3EChopra%20said%20on%20his%20YouTube%20channel.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChopra%20explained%20that%20Ashwin's%20accuracy%20to%20constantly%20hit%20the%20right%20areas%20is%20one%20of%20the%20reason's%20behind%20his%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHis%20quality%20is%20to%20keep%20bowling%20at%20one%20spot%20continuously.%20This%20job%20used%20to%20be%20very%20easy%20earlier%20but%20people%20don't%20do%20that%20these%20days.%20There%20are%20only%20three%20or%20four%20spinners%20who%20are%20able%20to%20pitch%20the%20ball%20at%20one%20spot%2C%20one%20is%20Ashwin%2C%20the%20second%20is%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Nathan%20Lyon%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1583-nathan-lyon-playerprofile%5C%22%3ENathan%20Lyon%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20third%20is%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Ravindra%20Jadeja%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F855-ravindra-jadeja-playerprofile%5C%22%3ERavindra%20Jadeja%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20it%20takes%20you%20a%20little%20more%20time%20to%20find%20the%20fourth.%20Ashwin%20bowled%20quite%20a%20lot%20from%20around%20the%20stumps.%20Subtle%20variations%2C%20he%20wasn't%20bowling%20carrom%20balls%20and%20all.%20A%20little%20drift%20in%20the%20air%2C%20slightly%20away%20from%20the%20batters%2C%20arm%20balls%2C%20a%20little%20turn%20and%20to%20get%20the%20ball%20to%20dip%20slightly%20with%20flight%20-%20he%20was%20in%20his%20elements%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Day%201%2C%20Ashwin%20started%20the%20day%20with%20the%20wickets%20of%20West%20Indies%20openers%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Tagenarine%20Chanderpaul%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F117136-tagenarine-chanderpaul-playerprofile%5C%22%3ETagenarine%20Chanderpaul%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Kraigg%20Brathwaite%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F1335-kraigg-brathwaite-playerprofile%5C%22%3EKraigg%20Brathwaite%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20the