he%20left%20Greens-European%20Free%20Alliance%2C%20the%20centre-right%20European%20People%E2%80%99s%20Party%20(EPP)%2C%20the%20centre-left%20Progressive%20Alliance%20of%20Socialists%20and%20Democrats%20(S%26amp%3BD)%2C%20the%20liberal%20Renew%20group%20and%20the%20right-wing%20European%20Conservatives%20and%20Reformists%20(ECR)%20group.%20Together%2C%20they%20account%20for%20around%2080%25%20of%20the%20MEPs%20in%20the%20705-member%20parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20following%20is%20a%20transcript%20of%20the%20debate%20of%20the%20European%20parliament%E2%80%99s%20plenary%20Session%20on%20Manipur%20on%20July%2012%2C%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20We%20can%20move%20on%20in%20the%20agenda%2C%20the%20next%20debate%20is%20on%20India%20and%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur.%20First%20of%20all%2C%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20Sven%20Simon%20as%20one%20of%20the%20authors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Sven%20Simon%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Madam%20President%20and%20colleagues.%20The%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20in%20the%20northeast%20of%20India%20is%20serious.%20Since%20May%2C%20in%20demonstrations%20between%20two%20population%20groups%20the%20mainly%20Hindu%20Meitei%20and%20the%20mainly%20Christian%20Kuki%2C%20over%20120%20people%20were%20killed%2C%20over%2050%2C000%20people%20are%20fleeing%2C%20over%20250%20churches%2C%20theological%20institutions%2C%20Christian%20schools%20and%20hospitals%20have%20been%20burnt%20down%20without%20the%20perpetrators%20being%20prevented%20by%20the%20local%20authorities.%20We%20call%20on%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20do%20everything%20to%20restore%20order%2C%20to%20bring%20the%20perpetrators%20to%20Justice%2C%20and%20to%20stop%20excessive%20violence.%20We%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20like%20to%20wag%20fingers%20at%20anybody%20from%20here%2C%20but%20with%20this%20resolution%20from%20the%20European%20Parliament%2C%20we%20call%20on%20the%20most%20populous%20democracy%20to%20do%20what%20it%20is%20duty-bound%20to%20do%20in%20its%20Constitution%3A%20to%20maintain%20religious%20freedom%20also%20for%20Christians%20in%20Manipur.%20One%20thing%2C%20colleagues%2C%20has%20irritated%20me%20with%20the%20negotiations%20with%20other%20groups.%20How%20difficult%20it%20is%20for%20the%20Greens%20and%20colleagues%20and%20those%20on%20the%20Left%20to%20say%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20Christians%20who%20are%20affected.%20They%20wriggle%20with%20platitudes%20about%20discrimination%20and%20religious%20intolerance%20and%20they%20can%E2%80%99t%20state%20what%20is%20obvious%20%E2%80%93%20persecutions%20of%20Christians%20are%20real%2C%20and%20it%20is%20our%20duty%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20they%20stop%2C%20also%20in%20Manipur.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20Mr%20Zeman.%20Pierre%20Larrouturou%20is%20the%20next%20speaker.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Pierre%20Larrouturou%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EFriends%2C%20in%20Manipur%20in%20Northeast%20India%2C%20violence%20has%20claimed%20more%20than%20120%20victims%20over%20two%20months.%20120%20people%20killed%2C%201%2C700%20houses%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20250%20churches%20%E2%80%93%20not%20just%20one%20or%20two%20churches%2C%20250%20churches%20%E2%80%93%20and%2040%20000%20people%20are%20displaced%20because%20they%E2%80%99ve%20run%20away%20from%20the%20violence%20to%20save%20their%20skins.%20This%20is%20a%20dramatic%20situation%2C%20we%20have%20to%20do%20everything%20possible%20to%20end%20violence.%20Since%20he%20entered%20power%20in%202014%2C%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20the%20prime%20minister%2C%20has%20been%20implementing%20a%20radical%20nationalist%20Hindu%20policy%20which%20has%20had%20terrible%20consequences%20%5Bfor%5D%20journalists%2C%20religious%20minorities%2C%20and%20human%20rights%20fighters.%20He%20always%20says%20that%20he%20is%20an%20heir%20to%20Mahatma%20Gandhi.%20We%20all%20admire%20%5Bhim%2C%5D%20he%20takes%20meditation%20time%2C%20he%20created%20a%20world%20yoga%20day.%20He%20seems%20kind%20and%20well-meaning.%20But%20in%20India%2C%20millions%20of%20Muslims%20and%20Christians%20suffer%20every%20single%20day%20because%20the%20government%20violates%20their%20most%20fundamental%20rights.%20The%20situation%20is%20serious.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20the%20European%20Parliament%20must%20vote%20tomorrow%20on%20a%20very%20clear%20resolution.%20It%20has%20to%20be%20clear%20in%20denouncing%20the%20nationalist%20discourse%20of%20Mr%20Modi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%20has%20to%20fully%20respect%20fundamental%20freedoms%2C%20freedom%20of%20expression%2C%20and%20religious%20freedoms%20for%20everyone.%20The%20resolution%20has%20to%20call%20for%20the%20violence%20to%20end%20immediately%20and%20to%20authorise%20humanitarian%20aid%20%5Bin%5D%20the%20presence%20of%20observers%20and%20journalists%20wherever%20necessary.%20They%20have%20to%20accept%20democratic%20functioning%2C%20no%20longer%20criminalise%20anyone%20who%20criticises%20government%20policy.%20That%E2%80%99s%20what%20democracy%20is%20about.%20The%20number%20of%20NGOs%20that%20are%20authorised%20to%20operate%20in%20India%20has%20been%20cut%20by%20three%20%5Btimes%5D%20in%20just%20a%20few%20years.%20They%20are%20trying%20to%20suffocate%20the%20NGOs%2C%20they%20are%20trying%20to%20suffocate%20democracy%20in%20civil%20society.%20There%20is%20no%20economic%20development%20without%20democracy.%20The%20European%20Parliament%20has%20to%20demand%20that%20respect%20for%20human%20rights%20is%20fully%20included%20in%20the%20EU-India%20partnership%2C%20including%20trade%20relations.%20That%20is%20in%20black%20and%20white%20in%20our%20text.%20We%20need%20to%20ensure%20that%20all%20our%20leaders%20talk%20about%20human%20rights%20when%20they%20visit%20India%2C%20publicly%20and%20systematically.%20Nobody%20is%20proposing%20breaking%20off%20relations%20with%20India.%20It%20is%20a%20great%20democracy%20but%20it%20has%20to%20be%20a%20better%20democracy%20and%20that%E2%80%99s%20why%20we%20support%20dialogue%20between%20India%20and%20Europe.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you.%20The%20next%20author%20on%20our%20list%20is%20Madame%20Alviina%20Alamets%C3%A4.%20One%20and%20a%20half%20minutes.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Alviina%20Alamets%C3%A4%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Honourable%20chair%20and%20colleagues.%20My%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20the%20families%20of%20the%20140%20people%20that%20have%20died%20in%20Manipur.%20This%20violence%20has%20led%20to%20the%20displacement%20of%20tens%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20I%20think%20that%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20must%20take%20action.%20There%20cannot%20be%20any%20more%20victims.%20Access%20to%20humanitarian%20aid%20and%20impartial%20observers%20to%20the%20area%20must%20be%20allowed.%20We%20should%20all%20be%20worried%20about%20the%20worsening%20human%20rights%20situation%20in%20India.%20Freedom%20of%20press%20has%20narrowed.%20Journalists%20and%20activists%20have%20been%20arrested%20for%20false%20reasons.%20Discrimination%20and%20hate%20have%20increased.%20And%20this%20is%20also%20what%20I%20saw%20personally%20when%20I%20visited%20India%20in%20December%20%5B2022%5D.%20This%20saddens%20me%20as%20India%20is%20a%20very%20important%20partner%20for%20us.%20Even%20India%20has%20to%20make%20human%20rights%20and%20democracy%20a%20fundamental%20part%20of%20their%20partnership%20in%20all%20regards%2C%20including%20trade.%20The%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20needs%20all%20of%20us%20to%20commit%20to%20open%2C%20transparent%2C%20and%20accountable%20ways%20to%20address%20conflict%20peacefully.%20The%20goal%20must%20be%20to%20end%20this%20violence%20and%20to%20bring%20about%20a%20peaceful%20resolution%20for%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20and%20for%20India%20to%20truly%20address%20all%20the%20root%20causes%20that%20are%20at%20the%20heart%20of%20these%20conflicts.%20I%20thank%20you%2C%20my%20colleagues%2C%20for%20cooperating%20on%20this%20and%20I%20send%20my%20deepest%20condolences%20to%20those%20who%20are%20suffering%20because%20of%20the%20human%20rights%20situation%20and%20the%20violence.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20the%20next%20author%2C%20Mr%20Bert-Jan%20Ruissen%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Bert-Jan%20Ruissen%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20president%2C%20commissioner%2C%20honourable%20members.%20When%20we%20discuss%20India%2C%20often%20we%20are%20talking%20about%20trade%20opportunities.%20Unfortunately%2C%20today%20we%E2%80%99re%20here%20to%20talk%20about%20human%20rights%2C%20about%20the%20situation%20in%20Manipur%2C%20where%20we%20have%20seen%20ethnic%20clashes%20taking%20on%20an%20increasing%20religious%20dimension.%20The%20events%20of%20the%20last%2010%20weeks%20are%20tragic.%20120%20lives%20lost%2C%2050%2C000%20people%20displaced%2C%20250%20churches%20destroyed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20this%20is%20not%20an%20isolated%20incident.%20Across%20India%2C%20those%20who%20are%20not%20Hindu%2C%20in%20particular%20Christians%2C%20are%20facing%20growing%20intolerance%2C%20violence%2C%20humiliation%2C%20discrimination.%20We%E2%80%99re%20seeing%20this%20in%20anti-conversion%20laws%20in%20different%20federal%20states.%20Our%20joint%20resolution%20is%20crystal%20clear%20%E2%80%93%20we%20are%20calling%20on%20India%20to%20do%20everything%20within%20its%20power%20to%20end%20ethnic%20and%20religious%20violence%2C%20to%20punish%20perpetrators%2C%20and%20end%20Hindu%20extremism.%20Without%20iron-clad%20guarantees%20in%20this%20area%2C%20we%20cannot%20talk%20about%20a%20new%20trade%20agreement%20with%20India.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20the%20next%20author%2C%20Mr%20Miguel%20Urb%C3%A1n%20Crespo%20for%20one%20minute.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Miguel%20Urb%C3%A1n%20Crespo%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20president.%20Ethnic%20minorities%20and%20religious%20minorities%20in%20India%20are%20systematically%20discriminated%20against.%20They%20are%20stigmatised%20and%20persecuted%20by%20the%20extreme%20right%20of%20Modi.%20This%20same%20applies%20to%20those%20who%20level%20criticism%20at%20the%20government.%20There%20are%20dozens%20of%20human%20rights%20defenders%20who%E2%80%99ve%20been%20put%20in%20prison%2C%20even%20though%20this%20parliament%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20mentioned%20them.%20What%20happens%20in%20Manipur%20is%20also%20the%20upshot%20of%20the%20xenophobic%20policies%20of%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20the%20very%20same%20government%20which%20issues%20veiled%20threats%20so%20that%20the%20kinds%20of%20debates%20we%20are%20having%20do%20not%20occur.%20Now%2C%20enough%20silent%20diplomacy.%20We%20must%20outright%20condemn%20the%20systematic%20abuses%20perpetrated%20by%20the%20Indian%20government%2C%20and%20we%20must%20clamour%20for%20the%20release%20of%20all%20political%20prisoners.%20Trade%20relations%20are%20political%20relations%20and%20must%20be%20tied%20to%20compliance%20with%20human%20rights.%20It%E2%80%99s%20high%20time%20to%20send%20a%20crystal%20clear%20message%20of%20support%20for%20the%20Indian%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20our%20next%20speaker%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20EPP%2C%20Madame%20Michaela%20%C5%A0ojdrov%C3%A1%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Michaela%20%C5%A0ojdrov%C3%A1%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20dear%20colleagues%2C%20Commissioner.%20The%20recent%20violent%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20have%20caused%20widespread%20devastation.%20Over%2050%2C000%20people%2C%20including%20a%20significant%20number%20of%20Christians%2C%20have%20been%20displaced%20and%20lives%20have%20been%20lost.%20Numerous%20religious%20symbols%20and%20places%20of%20worship%20have%20been%20targeted%20with%20more