20My%20colleague%2C%20Simon%2C%20has%20said%20he%20doesn%E2%80%99t%20want%20to%20wag%20his%20finger%20at%20India.%20He%20couldn%E2%80%99t%20do%20without%20wagging%20though%2C%20so%20he%20wagged%20his%20finger%20at%20the%20Greens.%20I%20will%20not%20retaliate.%20I%20will%20just%20say%2C%20we%20will%20defend%20religious%20freedom%20wherever%20it%20is%20endangered%2C%20be%20it%20Christians%20or%20otherwise.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20and%20now%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20ECR%20group%2C%20Mr%20Adam%20Bielan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Adam%20Bielan%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20Mr%20President.%20The%20situation%20in%20Manipur%20is%20deeply%20concerning.%20Since%20May%2C%20tensions%20between%20the%20mainly%20Hindu%20Meitei%20and%20mainly%20Christian%20Kuki%20communities%20have%20escalated%20to%20the%20most%20violent%20clashes%20in%20decades.%20Over%20140%20people%20have%20lost%20their%20lives%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20are%20displaced%2C%20and%20private%20and%20public%20property%20has%20been%20destroyed.%20Despite%20the%20gravity%20of%20the%20situation%2C%20authorities%20are%20not%20taking%20sufficient%20action%20and%20fostering%20peace%20dialogues.%20While%20the%20Manipur%20Tribal%20Forum%E2%80%99s%20plea%20for%20protection%20of%20the%20Kuki%20tribe%20by%20the%20Indian%20army%20has%20been%20rejected%20by%20the%20Supreme%20Court.%20We%2C%20therefore%2C%20urge%20all%20parties%20to%20cease%20hostilities%20and%20resolve%20the%20underlying%20regional%20and%20religious%20issues.%20The%20EU%20and%20its%20member%20states%20should%20collaborate%20with%20like-minded%20countries%20and%20organisations%20to%20assess%20possible%20further%20steps%20and%20continue%20to%20raise%20human%20rights%2C%20and%20especially%20religious%20freedom%2C%20concerns%20with%20the%20Indian%20authorities.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20on%20behalf%20of%20the%20EPP%20group%2C%20Mr%20Ji%C5%99%C3%AD%20Posp%C3%AD%C5%A1il%20for%20one%20minute.%3Cspan%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Ji%C5%99%C3%AD%20Posp%C3%AD%C5%A1il%3A%20%3C%2Fb%3EThank%20you%2C%20Mr%20President.%20Like%20my%20colleagues%2C%20I%20would%20like%20to%20support%20the%20draft%20resolution%20that%2C%20in%20my%20view%2C%20very%20much%20goes%20to%20the%20point.%20It%E2%80%99s%20up%20to%20date.%20India%20is%20the%20largest%20democracy%20in%20the%20world%2C%20a%20key%20partner%20of%20the%20EU%20in%20business.%20Democracy%20in%20recent%20years%20has%20worked%20in%20India%2C%20but%20democracy%20is%20also%20about%20human%20rights%20protection%2C%20and%20certainly%20there%20have%20been%20cases%20where%20human%20rights%20failed%20to%20be%20protected%2C%20especially%20those%20of%20religious%20minorities.%20We%20mentioned%20the%20Christian%20religious%20minority%20in%20the%20resolution%2C%20not%20only%20in%20one%20federal%20state%20of%20India%20but%20throughout%20the%20whole%20country.%20We%20must%20appeal%20to%20the%20central%20Indian%20government%2C%20to%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%2C%20that%20it%E2%80%99s%20impossible%20that%20a%20key%20partner%20of%20the%20EU%20not%20guarantee%20key%20human%20rights%20of%20anybody%2C%20whether%20they%20are%20of%20Christian%20religion%20or%20anybody%20else.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20Mr%20Il%C4%8Di%C4%87%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Ladislav%20Il%C4%8Di%C4%87%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Ladies%20and%20gentlemen.%20Although%20dramatic%20violence%20in%20India%20in%20Manipur%20began%20because%20of%20land%20ownership%2C%20it%20seems%20that%20very%20quickly%20it%20also%20became%20religiously%20conditioned%20violence.%20Over%20250%20churches%20were%20attacked%2C%20numerous%20cemeteries%20and%20parish%20houses.%20India%20is%20an%20important%20partner%20to%20the%20European%20Union.%20But%20if%20we%20as%20a%20Christian%20community%20can%20respect%20other%20faiths%20and%20identities%2C%20we%20must%20ask%20our%20partners%20to%20do%20the%20same.%20I%20propose%20an%20urgent%20visit%20by%20the%20European%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20Religious%20Freedoms%20to%20India.%20And%20the%20way%20the%20Indian%20government%20will%20treat%20this%20proposal%20will%20show%20whether%20the%20authorities%20there%20are%20for%20the%20time%20being%20only%20powerless%20in%20such%20cases%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20knowingly%20allow%20the%20persecution%20of%20religious%20minorities%20by%20radical%20groups.%20Our%20message%20must%20be%20clear%20we%20will%20not%20turn%20our%20heads%20away%20from%20violence%20and%20we%20will%20not%20turn%20our%20backs%20on%20persecuted%20Christians.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%2C%20and%20now%20I%20give%20the%20floor%20to%20Madame%20Miriam%20Lexmann%20for%20one%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Miriam%20Lexmann%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20chair%2C%20colleagues.%20The%20state%20of%20freedom%20of%20religion%20and%20belief%20in%20a%20society%20is%20an%20important%20litmus%20test%20to%20the%20state%20of%20other%20fundamental%20freedoms.%20Therefore%2C%20while%20Indian%20officials%20often%20like%20to%20boast%20that%20the%20country%20is%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20democracy%2C%20intolerance%20and%20violence%20against%20religious%20minorities%20paint%20a%20different%20picture.%20In%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20at%20least%20100%20people%20are%20dead%2C%20tens%20of%20thousands%20displaced%2C%20hundreds%20of%20houses%20belonging%20to%20Christians%20destroyed%2C%20along%20with%20250%20churches%2C%20theological%20institutions%2C%20schools%20and%20hospitals%2C%20as%20well%20as%20several%20temples.%20These%20attacks%20against%20Christians%20are%20not%20isolated%20incidents.%20They%20are%20organised%2C%20leaving%20behind%20destruction%20and%20shattered%20lives.%20The%20EU%20cannot%20close%20its%20eyes%20to%20these%20crimes.%20That%E2%80%99s%20why%20I%20call%20on%20our%20Special%20Envoy%20for%20Freedom%20of%20Religion%20and%20the%20EES%20to%20communicate%20clearly%20to%20the%20Indian%20authorities%20the%20need%20to%20stop%20this%20violence%20and%20to%20provide%20the%20necessary%20support%20to%20the%20victims%20immediately.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EChair%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much%2C%20now%20colleagues%20start%20the%20%5Bunclear%5D%20procedure.%20I%20have%20one%20speaker%20on%20the%20%5Bunclear%5D%20procedure%2C%20and%20I%20will%20give%20a%20floor%20to%20Eugen%20Tomac.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3EMEP%20Eugen%20Tomac%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20very%20much.%20We%20do%20have%20to%20show%20our%20solidarity%20to%20people%20who%20find%20themselves%20in%20such%20a%20difficult%20situation.%20What%20is%20happening%20in%20Manipur%20is%20reflecting%20the%20reality%20that%20very%20often%20member%20states%20won%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%2C%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20look%20at%20in%20depth%20and%20I%20think%20the%20European%20Commission%20has%20the%20obligation%20now%20to%20act%20more%20strongly%20in%20its%20relations%20with%20the%20Indian%20government.%20They%20have%20to%20ask%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20protect%20all%20Indian%20citizens%2C%20including%20Christians%20because%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20Indians%20are%20displaced%2C%20more%20than%20250%20churches%20have%20been%20destroyed%2C%20and%20all%20of%20this%20does%20mean%20that%20the%20European%20Commission%20has%20to%20act%20they%20have%20to%20act%20to%20protect.%20It%20is%20not%20the%20fault%20of%20these%20people%20that%20the%20Government%20is%20not%20in%20a%20position%20to%20protect%20the%20Constitution.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cb%3ECommissioner%20Mairead%20McGuinness%3A%3C%2Fb%3E%20Thank%20you%20President%2C%20Honourable%20Members.%20I%20really%20would%20like%20to%20reassure%20you%20that%20the%20European%20Union%20is%20following%20the%20situation%20in%20the%20state%20of%20Manipur%20closely%2C%20and%20we%20are%20very%20saddened%2C%20deeply%20saddened%2C%20by%20the%20large%20number%20of%20deaths%20and%20of%20injured%20and%20displaced%20persons%20since%20violence%20erupted%20in%20Manipur%20at%20the%20beginning%20of%20May.%20The%20Indian%20authorities%20have%20taken%20a%20number%20of%20measures%20to%20address%20this%20very%20tense%20situation.%20A%20commission%20of%20inquiry%20has%20been%20set%20up%20to%20investigate%20instance%20of%20violence.%20A%20peace%20committee%20has%20been%20established%20with%20broad%20participation%20to%20facilitate%20peace%20negotiations%20and%20dialogue%20between%20the%20conflicting%20groups.%20We%20hope%20that%20these%20measures%20will%20very%20soon%20bring%20results%20so%20that%20this%20wave%20of%20violence%20and%20the%20profound%20mistrust%20between%20the%20communities%20comes%20to%20an%20end.%20India%20is%20a%20strategic%20partner%20of%20the%20EU.%20Our%20relations%20are%20based%20on%20mutual%20respect%2C%20and%20the%20protection%20and%20promotion%20of%20Human%20Rights%20and%20fundamental%20freedoms%20are%20at%20the%20core%20of%20our%20partnership.%20We%20discuss%20regularly%20with%20India%20the%20challenges%20and%20best%20approaches%20on%20human%20rights%20in%20both%20Europe%20and%20India.%20The%20annual%20EU-India%20Human%20Rights%20dialogue%20provides%20a%20good%20platform%20for%20frank%20and%20open%20discussion%20between%20us.%20The%20last%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20July%20of%20last%20year%2C%20and%20the%20next%20one%20should%20happen%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20year.%20The%20EU%20is%20ready%20to%20support%20our%20Indian%20friends%20if%20requested%20in%20their%20efforts%20towards%20rebuilding%20peace%20and%20trust%20between%20the%20different%20groups%20in%20Manipur.%20Thank%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689252013000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13175306%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-5.52.20-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Ffull-text-european-mp-debate-manipur-violence%22