attached).%20It%20may%20be%20noted%20that%20the%20amount%20allocated%20through%20LoA%20will%20not%20be%20available%20for%20expenditure%2Fre-appropriation%20by%20the%20functional%20Ministry%2FDepartment%20in%20the%20current%20FY%202023-24.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20CBC%E2%80%99s%20Budget%20for%202023-24%20approved%20by%20Parliament%20is%20Rs%20200%20crore.%20With%20the%20May%2019th%2C%202023%20order%20of%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20the%20Budget%20for%20CBC%20for%20the%20current%20year%20will%20suddenly%20zoom%20to%20more%20than%20Rs%20750%20crores%2C%E2%80%9D%20Ramesh%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EParliament%20votes%20Budgets%20for%20all%20Departments%20and%20Ministries%20of%20the%20Government%20of%20India.%20Each%20programme%2Fscheme%20has%20a%20distinct%20Budget%20Head.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20on%20May%2019%2C%202023%20in%20an%20unprecedented%20move%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Finance%20has%20ordered%20that%2040%25%20of%20the%20funds%20voted%20by%20Parliament%20for%20%E2%80%98Advertising%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FYusTFtx52R%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FYusTFtx52R%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20(%40Jairam_Ramesh)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FJairam_Ramesh%2Fstatus%2F1679355833711296513%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2013%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20Congress%20has%20alleged%20that%20the%20money%20will%20be%20used%20by%20the%20CBC%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%202024%20general%20election%20campaign.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHe%20claimed%20that%20the%20CBC%2C%20along%20with%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigation%20(CBI)%20and%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20%E2%80%9Cwill%20be%20the%20spearhead%E2%80%9D%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99