00%20actors%20and%20television%20and%20radio%20presenters%20as%20well%20as%C2%A0other%20media%20professionals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20are%20SAG-AFTRA%E2%80%99s%20demands%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20union%20is%20demanding%20higher%20compensation%20from%20streaming%20services%20as%20well%20as%C2%A0higher%20pay%20to%20counteract%20inflation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20salaries%20when%20working%2C%20actors%20earn%20%E2%80%9Cresiduals%E2%80%9D%20every%20time%20a%20production%20they%20star%20in%20is%20aired%20on%20a%20network%20or%20cable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20streaming%20services%20such%20as%20Netflix%20and%20Disney%2B%20do%20not%20disclose%20viewing%20figures%20and%20pay%20actors%20the%20same%20flat%20rate%20regardless%20of%20viewership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%C2%A0is%20also%20demanding%20the%20implementation%20of%20safeguards%20around%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fartificial-intelligence%2Ft-42133476%5C%22%3Euse%20of%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Actors%20want%20assurances%20that%20their%20digital%20images%20will%20not%20be%20used%20without%20their%20permission.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20SAG-AFTRA%20TV%2FTheatrical%2FStreaming%20Negotiating%20Committee%20has%20agreed%20to%20the%20AMPTP%E2%80%99s%20last-minute%20request%20for%20federal%20mediation%20and%20has%20reaffirmed%20the%20negotiating%20committee%E2%80%99s%20dedication%20to%20securing%20a%20fair%20deal%20(1%2F7)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9gXZV6ZcRX%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F9gXZV6ZcRX%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20SAG-AFTRA%20(%40sagaftra)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fsagaftra%2Fstatus%2F1679166776897306624%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EJuly%2012%2C%202023%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20has%20happened%20in%20negotiations%20thus%20far%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Tuesday%2C%20union%20negotiators%20agreed%20to%20a%20studio%20request%20to%20bring%20in%20a%20federal%20mediator.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESAG-AFTRA%20said%20that%20studio%20representatives%20had%20%E2%80%9Cabused%20our%20trust%E2%80%9D%20by%20leaking%20information%20to%20the%20media%2C%20adding%20that%20there%20would%20be%20no%20change%20in%20the%20Wednesday%20night%20deadline%20that%20would%20trigger%20a%20strike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20not%20confident%20that%20the%20employers%20have%20any%20intention%20of%20bargaining%20toward%20an%20agreement%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20union%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20late%20Tuesday.%20%E2%80%9CTime%20is%20running%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%98Double%20strike%E2%80%99%20could%20bring%20almost%20all%20productions%20to%20a%20halt%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20strike%20threatened%20by%20SAG-AFTRA%20follows%20similar%20action%20by%20the%20industry%E2%80%99s%20main%20writers%E2%80%99%20union.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarly%20in%20May%2C%20the%20roughly%2011%2C500%20members%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.dw.com%2Fen%2Fhollywood-writers-to-go-on-strike-over-pay%2Fa-65488752%5C%22%3EWriters%20Guild%20of%20America%20(WGA)%20went%20on%20strike%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20disrupted%20most%20production%20for%20the%20autumn%20TV%20season%20and%20the%20filming%20of%20some%20big-budget%20movies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Alliance%20of%20Motion%20Picture%20and%20Television%20Producers%20(AMPTP)%20said%20it%20had%20offered%20%E2%80%9Cgenerous%E2%80%9D%20pay%20raises%20but%20could%20not%20agree%20to%20all%20of%20the%20demands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20SAG-AFTRA%20announces%20a%20walkout%2C%20this%20will%20lead%20to%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdouble%20strike%E2%80%9D%20not%20seen%20in%20Hollywood%20since%201960%20and%20halt%20most%20US%20film%20and%20television%20productions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3