ng%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20Police%20Scotland%20statement%20said%20with%20reference%20to%20the%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20Sunday%2C%20a%20female%20journalist%20and%20author%20alleged%20that%20Kohli%20made%20unwanted%20and%20aggressive%20sexual%20advances%20towards%20her%20after%20inviting%20her%20for%20an%20interview%20at%20his%20London%20flat%20when%20she%20was%2022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E'The%20Times'%20reported%20that%20the%2036-year-old%20said%20Kohli's%20conduct%20left%20her%20so%20distressed%20that%20she%20tried%20to%20escape%20out%20of%20his%20bathroom%20window.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20newspaper%20also%20reported%20that%20a%20former%20entertainment%20worker%20alleged%20that%20Kohli%20had%20attacked%20her%20in%20a%20lift%20during%20the%20Edinburgh%20Fringe%20in%202013%20when%20she%20was%2019%20and%20he%20was%2044.%20The%20broadcaster%20was%20a%20performer%20at%20the%20festival%20at%20the%20time.%20Since%20then%2C%20the%20Pleasance%20Theatre%20Trust%2C%20which%20operates%20several%20venues%20during%20the%20annual%20Scottish%20arts%20festival%20and%20has%20previously%20hosted%20performances%20by%20Kohli%2C%20indicated%20he%20would%20no%20longer%20be%20welcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20consider%20behaviour%20of%20this%20kind%20to%20be%20abhorrent.%20Anyone%20found%20to%20have%20committed%20sexual%20assault%20or%20inappropriate%20sexual%20behaviour%20is%20not%2C%20and%20never%20will%20be%2C%20welcome%20at%20the%20Pleasance%2C%26quot%3B%20Anthony%20Alderson%2C%20director%20of%20the%20trust%2C%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBack%20in%202020%2C%20Kohli%20apologised%20for%20making%20women%20feel%20%26quot%3Bintimidated%2C%20undermined%20and%20undervalued%26quot%3B%20and%20the%20broadcaster%20had%20cut%20ties%20with%20the%20food%20writer%20and%20reality%20show%20contestant%20at%20the%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPreviously%20in%202009%2C%20Kohli%20was%20suspended%20from%20working%20on%20the%20BBC%20magazine%20programme%20'The%20One%20Show'%2