ession.%20Only%20when%20both%20aspects%20of%20adolescent's%20rights%20are%20recognised%2C%20human%20sexual%20dignity%20can%20be%20considered%20to%20be%20fully%20respected%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20made%20the%20remarks%20in%20an%20appeal%20filed%20by%20a%2025-year-old%20man%20challenging%20a%20February%202019%20order%20of%20a%20special%20court%20convicting%20him%20for%20raping%20a%2017-year-old%20girl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20man%20and%20the%20girl%20had%20claimed%20they%20were%20in%20a%20consensual%20relationship.%20The%20girl%20in%20her%20submission%20before%20the%20special%20court%20claimed%20that%20under%20the%20Muslim%20law%2C%20she%20was%20considered%20a%20major%20and%20hence%20she%20had%20'Nikah'%20with%20the%20accused%20man.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Dangre%20quashed%20the%20conviction%20order%20and%20acquitted%20the%20man%2C%20noting%20the%20evidence%20on%20record%20has%20clearly%20made%20out%20a%20case%20for%20consensual%20sex%2C%20and%20ordered%20for%20him%20to%20be%20released%20from%20jail.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20age%20of%20consent%20necessarily%20must%20be%20distinguished%20from%20the%20age%20of%20marriage%20as%20sexual%20acts%20do%20not%20happen%20only%20in%20the%20confines%20of%20marriage%2C%20and%20not%20only%20the%20society%20but%20the%20judicial%20system%20must%20take%20note%20of%20this%20important%20aspect%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20the%20time%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20has%20been%20increased%20by%20various%20statutes%20in%20India.%20It%20was%20maintained%20at%2016%20from%201940%20till%202012%2C%20when%20the%20POCSO%20Act%20raised%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20to%2018%20years%2C%20probably%20one%20of%20the%20highest%20ages%20globally%2C%20as%20majority%20of%20the%20countries%20have%20set%20their%20age%20of%20consent%20in%20the%20range%20of%2014%20to%2016%20years%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20in%20countries%20like%20Germany%2C%20Italy%2C%20Portugal%20and%20Hungary%2C%20children%20in%20the%20age%20group%20of%2014%20are%20considered%20capable%20of%20giving%20consent%20to%20sex.%20In%20London%20and%20Wales%2C%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20is%2016%20and%20in%20Japan%20it%20is%2013%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Dangre%20said%20the%20scenario%20which%20emerges%20is%20that%20a%20girl%20under%20the%20age%20of%2018%20is%20expected%20not%20to%20indulge%20herself%20into%20a%20sexual%20activity%20and%20even%20if%20she%20does%20so%2C%20being%20an%20active%20participant%20in%20the%20activity%2C%20her%20consent%20is%20immaterial%20and%20is%20no%20consent%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20a%20result%20of%20this%20scenario%2C%20even%20if%20a%20boy%20aged%2020%20indulges%20with%20a%20girl%20aged%2017%20years%20and%20364%20days%2C%20he%20would%20be%20found%20guilty%20of%20committing%20rape%20upon%20her%20despite%20the%20girl%20clearly%20admitting%20that%20she%20was%20equally%20involved%20in%20the%20act%20of%20sex.%20The%20minor%20is%20not%20considered%20to%20be%20capable%20enough%20to%20give%20valid%20consent%20in%20the%20eyes%20of%20law%20for%20entering%20into%20consensual%20sex%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20HC%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20case%20of%20physical%20attraction%20or%20infatuation%20always%20comes%20forth%2C%20when%20a%20teenager%20enters%20into%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20and%20it%20is%20high%20time%20that%20our%20country%20is%20also%20cognizant%20of%20happenings%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Justice%20Dangre%20said%20in%20the%20judgment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20necessary%20for%20our%20country%20to%20look%20around%20and%20observe%20all%20that%20is%20happening%20around%20the%20world%20in%20this%20regard%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20one%20thing%20is%20sure%20that%20in%20this%20whole%20scenario%2C%20if%20a%20young%20boy%20is%20castigated%20for%20being%20guilty%20of%20committing%20rape%20on%20a%20minor%20girl%2C%20merely%20because%20she%20is%20below%2018%20but%20an%20equal%20participant%20in%20the%20act%2C%20he%20would%20suffer%20a%20severe%20dent%20which%20he%20will%20have%20to%20carry%20lifelong%2C%20the%20judge%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BUltimately%2C%20it%20is%20for%20Parliament%20to%20ponder%20upon%20the%20said%20issue%2C%20being%20cognizant%20of%20the%20cases%20which%20are%20coming%20before%20the%20courts%2C%20with%20a%20huge%20chunk%20being%20of%20romantic%20relationships%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20cases%20of%20teenagers%20who%20fall%20for%20attraction%20of%20the%20opposite%20sex%20and%20enter%20into%20a%20sexual%20relationship%20out%20of%20impulsiveness%2C%20only%20one%20has%20to%20take%20the%20consequences%20on%20being%20charged%20for%20committing%20an%20offence%20of%20rape%20though%20the%20other%20had%20also%20indulged%20into%20the%20same%20act%2C%20Justice%20Dangre%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BA%20provision%20which%20does%20not%20take%20into%20consideration%20our%20societal%20realities%20and%20proceeds%20on%20an%20assumption%20that%20every%20sexual%20indulgence%20with%20a%20minor%2C%20irrespective%20of%20whether%20she%20was%20capable%20of%20being%20an%20equal%20participant%20in%20the%20act%2C%20has%20definitely%20created%20a%20situation%2C%20resulting%20in%20acquittal%20of%20the%20accused%20in%20cases%20of%20consensual%20sexual%20relationship%2C%20where%20the%20gap%20in%20the%20age%20of%20accused%20and%20that%20of%20victim%20is%20small%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20judgment%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20court%20said%20the%20POCSO%20Act%2C%20though%20definitely%20intended%20to%20target%20sexual%20exploitation%20of%20children%2C%20however%20has%20created%20a%20grey%20area%20as%20it%20has%20definitely%20resulted%20in%20criminalising%20consensual%20adolescence%2F%20teenage%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAdolescence%20is%20a%20phase%20of%20transition%20during%20which%20major%20developments%20of%20sexuality%20take%20place%2C%20with%20puberty%20being%20marked%20as%20a%20major%20landmark%20in%20the%20journey%20of%20sexuality.%20It%20is%20during%20this%20period%20cognitive%20development%20takes%20place%20and%20it%20results%20into%20development%20of%20thinking%20and%20reasoning%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20court%20said.%20Adolescence%20is%20a%20period%20during%20which%20an%20individual's%20thought%20perception%20as%20well%20as%20response%20get%20coloured%20sexually.%20It%20is%20an%20age%20to%20explore%20and%20understand%20sexuality.%20Sexual%20curiosity%20in%20adolescence%20often%20leads%20to%20exposure%20to%20pornography%2C%20indulgence%20in%20sexual%20activities%2C%20and%20also%20increase%20in%20the%20vulnerability%20for%20sexual%20abuse%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20era%20where%20adolescents%20have%20free%20access%20to%20internet%2C%20which%20creates%20a%20deep%20impact%20upon%20their%20minds%2C%20coupled%20with%20inquisitiveness%20about%20sex%20along%20with%20physical%20attraction%20towards%20other%20sex%20and%20infatuation%2C%20which%20is%20a%20matter%20of%20research%20as%20the%20question%20of%20youthful%20sexuality%20has%20to%20be%20tackled%20in%20the%20current%20society%20by%20appropriately%20moderating%20their%20behaviour%2C%20the%20high%20court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bench%20said%20while%20all%20children%20are%20entitled%20to%20be%20protected%20from%20sexual%20violence%2C%20such%20protection%20should%20also%20enable%20young%20people%20to%20extend%20their%20boundaries%2C%20exercise%20choices%20and%20engage%20in%20necessary%20risk%20taking%20without%20exposing%20them%20to%20inappropriate%20response%2C%20harm%20and%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20penal%20approach%20towards%20adolescents'%20sexuality%20has%20impacted%20their%20life%20to%20a%20barrier%20free%20access%20to%20sexual%20and%20reproductive%20health%20services%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20High%20Court%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20said%20criminalisation%20of%20romantic%20relationships%20has%20overburdened%20the%20criminal%20justice%20system%20by%20consuming%20significant%20time%20of%20the%20judiciary%2C%20police%20and%20the%20child%20protection%20system.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20balance%20between%20protection%20of%20the%20vulnerable%20class%20and%20that%20capable%20of%20exercising%20the%20power%20to%20decide%20what%20is%20right%20for%20them%20must%20be%20necessarily%20struck%2C%20the%20court%20said.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689240420000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-07%2Fl176bpe_couple-hands-bedroom-sex-generic_625x300_13_July_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-time-parliament-reduces-age-of-consent-for-sexual-relationships-bombay-high-court-4203352%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Bombay%20High%20Court%20has%20said%20several%20countries%20have%20reduced%20the%20age%20of%20consent%20for%20adolescents%20to%20enter%20into%20a%20consensual%20sexual%20relationship%20and%20it%20is%20high%20time%20our%20country%20and%20Parliament%20are%20also%20cognisant%20of%20happenings%20around%20the%20world.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-time-parliament-reduces-age-of-consent-for-sexual-relationships-bombay-high-court-4203352%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-time-parliament-reduces-age-of-consent-for-sexual-relationships-bombay-high-court-4203352%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhigh-time-parliament-reduces-age-of-consent-for-sexual-relationships-bombay-high-court-4203352%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Rishabh's%20fans%20troll%20Urvashi%2C%20here's%20why!%22%2C%22c