nipur.%20The%20groups%20deny%20this%20allegation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESingh%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Hindu%3C%2Fem%3E%20that%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20FIR%20and%20that%20he%20is%20%E2%80%9Cnot%20bothered%E2%80%9D%20by%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20ethnic%20clashes%20between%20the%20Meitei%20and%20Kuki%20communities%20in%20Manipur%2C%20which%20have%20been%20ongoing%20since%20May%203%2C%20have%20claimed%20more%20than%20140%20lives%20and%20displaced%20more%20than%2050%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20Kukis%20%E2%80%93%20a%20leading%20academic%20and%20two%20activists%20%E2%80%93%20have%20been%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Fhyderabad-university-professor-two-kuki-activists-summoned-by-imphal-court-for-interviews-to-the-wire%5C%22%3Esummoned%20by%20an%20Imphal%20court%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20statements%20they%20made%20in%20interviews%20with%20Karan%20Thapar.%20The%20three%20are%20University%20of%20Hyderabad%20professor%20Kham%20Khan%20Suan%20Hausing%3B%20the%20convenor%20of%20the%20Kuki%20Women%E2%80%99s%20Forum%20Mary%20Grace%20Zou%3B%20and%20the%20general%20secretary%20of%20the%20Kuki%20People%E2%80%99s%20Alliance%20Wilson%20Lalam%20Hangshing.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689235827000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13132622%2FKT-6-June.01_15_29_19.Still003.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-meitei-leepun-pramot-singh-case-enmity%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20complaint%2C%20filed%20by%20a%20Kuki%20students'%20group%2C%20cites%20statements%20made%20by%20Pramot%20Singh%20in%20his%20interview%20with%20Karan%20Thapar%20and%20tweets%20that%20he%20posted%20before%20the%20ethnic%20clashes%20began%20in%20Manipur.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fmanipur-meitei-leepun-pramot-singh-case-enmity%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Ukraine%20war%3A%20Russian%20general%20fired%20after%20criticising%20army%20leaders%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689235734000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2FA33A%2Fproduction%2F_130368714_popov.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66185545%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Gen%20Ivan%20Popov%20says%20he%20refused%20to%20keep%20quiet%20over%20issues%20at%20the%20front%20line%20in%20Ukraine.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A223%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66185545%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-co-uk.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66185545.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.co.uk%2Fnews%2Fworld-europe-66185545.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Did%20you%20know%20Kamal%20Haasan%E2%80%99s%20make%20up%20for%20Indian%202%20takes%20four%20hours%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689235472000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-101722832%2Cimgsize-35198.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-kamal-haasans-make-up-for-indian-2-takes-four-hours-exclusive-details%2Farticleshow%2F101722838.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kamal%20Hassan%20is%20all%20set%20to%20enthrall%20audience%20as%20he%20revives%20his%20character%20Senapathy%20from%20Indian%20(%201996).%20The%20actor%20spends%20nearly%207%20hours%20on%20everyday%20basis%20to%20apply%20and%20remove%20the%20make-up%20as%20he%20plays%20a%2090%20year%20old%20in%20the%20film.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22JIGAR%20SHAH%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fdid-you-know-kamal-haasans-make-up-for-indian-2-takes-four-hours-exclusive-details%2Farticleshow%2F101722838.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22EU%20FTA%20Talks%3A%20Government%20Mum%20on%20Hiring%20Lobby%20Firm%20Which%20Lists%20'Services%20to%20India'%20on%20Website%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10140837%2Frti-cic-right-to-information.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20government%20has%20refused%20to%20admit%20that%20it%20has%20hired%20the%20Brussels-based%20lobby%20firm%20Alber%20%26amp%3B%20Geiger%20to%20lobby%20for%20it%20in%20the%20India-European%20Union%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20(FTA)%20even%20as%20the%20firm%20itself%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Falbergeiger.com%2Fwins%2Ffree-trade-agreement-between-india-and-the-eu%2F%5C%22%3Elists%20its%20services%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20and%20its%20triumphs%20in%20shaping%20and%20steering%20EU%20lawmakers%20to%20support%20the%20FTA%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20May%2020%2C%20the%20Citizen%E2%80%99s%20Watch%20on%20FTAs%2C%20a%20group%20of%20foreign%20trade%20policy%20experts%2C%20rights%20activists%20for%20women%20and%20workers%2C%20transparency%20and%20human%20rights%20advocates%2C%20had%20filed%20three%20Right%20to%20Information%20applications%20seeking%20information%20on%20the%20name%20of%20every%20external%20agency%20which%20has%20been%20hired%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20obtaining%20advice%20and%20support%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20free%20trade%20negotiations%20between%20India%20and%20other%20countries%20since%20April%202019%2C%20to%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20detailed%20note%2C%20the%20Citizen%E2%80%99s%20Watch%20group%20outlined%20the%20necessity%20for%20transparency%20in%20the%20ongoing%20dialogues%20between%20India%20and%20the%20EU.%20This%2C%20it%20said%2C%20is%20essential%20to%20understand%20the%20social%20impact%20on%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20stakeholders%2C%20from%20farmers%20to%20fisherfolk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20Venkatesh%20Nayak%2C%20who%20filed%20the%20RTI%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CHaving%20found%20from%20Alber%20%26amp%3B%20Geiger%E2%80%99s%20website%20that%20they%20provided%20assistance%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20to%20assuage%20concerns%20of%20members%20of%20the%20European%20Parliament%20(MEP)%20regarding%20the%20human%20rights%20situation%20in%20India%20in%20the%20ongoing%20FTA%20negotiations%2C%20we%20filed%20two%20RTI%20applications%20on%20this%20subject%20%E2%80%93%20one%20asking%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20if%20any%20external%20organisation%20was%20hired%20to%20help%20with%20the%20FTA%20negotiations%2C%20and%20the%20second%2C%20with%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20in%20Brussels.%20The%20third%20RTI%20application%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20the%20other%20two%2C%20and%20was%20submitted%20to%20the%20Union%20commerce%20ministry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20far%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20not%20revealed%20any%20information%20on%20the%20FTA%20discussions.%20The%20Citizen%E2%80%99s%20Watch%20has%20cited%20this%20as%20one%20of%20the%20reasons%20why%20it%20filed%20the%20RTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInformation%20on%20the%20talks%20is%20vital%20to%20various%20stakeholders%20including%20millions%20of%20farmers%2C%20workers%2C%20artisans%2C%20fisherfolk%2C%20small%20business%20owners%20and%20workers%2C%20gig%20workers%2C%20home-based%20workers%20and%20others%2C%20says%20Nayak.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20as%20the%20European%20Commission%20(EC)%20is%20holding%20consultations%20and%20dialogues%20with%20civil%20society%20stakeholders%20in%20the%20EU%20member-states%20on%20the%20social%20impact%20assessment%20(SIA)%20of%20the%20proposed%20FTA%20with%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nayak%2C%20%E2%80%9Cthere%E2%80%99s%20a%20complete%20lack%20of%20transparency%20and%20non-inclusive%20consultation%20processes%20adopted%20by%20the%20Union%20Government%20here%20in%20the%20negotiations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20so%2C%20the%20first%20RTI%20application%20filed%20on%20May%2015%2C%202023%2C%20asked%20not%20only%20for%20the%20names%20and%20address%20of%20any%20external%20agency%20if%20hired%20by%20MEA%2C%20it%20also%20asked%20for%20copies%20of%20all%20official%20records%20of%20the%20task%20being%20carried%20out%20and%2C%20the%20expenditure%20incurred%20in%20hiring%20any%20external%20agencies%20till%20date.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124854%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-12.47.58-PM.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124854%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-12.47.58-PM.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124854%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-12.47.58-PM-300x158.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124854%2FScreenshot-2023-07-13-at-12.47.58-PM-1024x540.png%201024w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-662967%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22633%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EA%20screengrab%20of%20Alber%20%26amp%3B%20Geiger%E2%80%99s%20webpage%2C%20listing%20India-EU%20FTA%20talks%20as%20one%20of%20its%20%E2%80%98Wins%E2%80%99.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20did%20the%20MEA%20respond%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20reply%20within%20two%20weeks%2C%20on%20May%2029%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said%20it%20has%20not%20hired%20the%20services%20of%20any%20agency%20%E2%80%9Cfor%20obtaining%20advice%20in%20relation%20to%20free%20trade%20negotiation%20between%20India%20and%20other%20countries.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20the%20question%20on%20budgetary%20allotment%20for%20the%20hiring%20of%20an%20external%20agency%2C%20the%20MEA%20said%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20request%20for%20information%20is%20transferred%20to%20Finance%20Division%20of%20MEA%20to%20directly%20convey%20it%20to%20the%20RTI%20applicant%E2%80%A6The%20desired%20information%20is%20available%20in%20public%20domain%20on%20the%20official%20website%20of%20this%20Ministry.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizen%E2%80%99s%20Watch%20filed%20a%20second%20RTI%20on%20June%205%2C%20with%20the%20same%20queries%2C%20this%20time%20to%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20to%20the%20EU%20in%20Brussels.%20But%20unlike%20the%20first%20time%20where%20the%20MEA%20actually%20responded%20promptly%2C%20the%20Central%20Public%20Information%20Officer%20(CPIO)%20who%20is%20the%20official%20authorised%20to%20respond%2C%20simply%20rejected%20the%20entire%20RTI%20application%20under%20Section%208(1)%20of%20the%20RTI%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20this%20section%2C%20an%20RTI%20application%20can%20be%20rejected%20if%20the%20information%20asked%20relates%20to%20personal%20information%20and%20which%20has%20no%20relationship%20to%20any%20public%20activity%20or%20interest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESays%20Nayak%2C%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20simply%20ridiculous%2C%20to%20say%20the%20least%2C%20because%20the%2010%20clauses%20which%20make%20up%20Section%208(1)%20contain%20more%20than%2030%20grounds%20for%20refusing%20access%20to%20information.%20To%20state%20that%20all%20of%20them%20will%20be%20attracted%20by%20the%20RTI%20queries%20is%20absurd.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20so%2C%20says%20Nayak%2C%20if%20the%20MEA%2C%20the%20Embassy%E2%80%99s%20parent%20ministry%20can%20reply%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20absolutely%20no%20reason%20why%20the%20latter%20cannot%20do%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Citizen%E2%80%99s%20Watch%20then%20filed%20a%20third%20RTI%20application%20also%20on%20June%205%2C%20with%20the%20commerce%20ministry%2C%20with%20the%20same%20questions%20put%20to%20the%20MEA%20and%20the%20Indian%20Embassy%20to%20the%20EU%2C%20asking%20%E2%80%9Cif%20any%20external%20agency%20was%20hired%20by%20the%20ministry%20for%20the%20purpose%20of%20obtaining%20advice%20and%20support%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20FTA%20negotiations%20between%20India%20and%20the%20EU%20till%20date.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RTI%20application%20also%20requested%20information%20on%20the%20detailed%20demand%20for%20grants%20(DDG)%20if%20any%2C%20from%20the%20ministry.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20its%20reply%20on%20June%2014%2C%20the%20CPIO%20attached%20to%20the%20commerce%20ministry%20was%20categorical%20when%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20been%20directed%20to%20answer%20specifically%20on%20budgetary%20allocation%2C%20and%20that%20relevant%20information%20was%20available%20on%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20website.%20Nayak%20says%20that%20while%20he%20is%20still%20to%20get%20down%20to%20locate%20the%20information%20on%20the%20ministry%E2%80%99s%20website%2C%20the%20RTI%20queries%20about%20hiring%20an%20external%20agency%20were%20transferred%20to%20another%20CPIO%20in%20the%20department.%20The%2030-day%20deadline%20ends%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20for%20the%20India-EU%20FTA%20talks%2C%20the%20EU%20website%20has%20been%20open%20to%20its%20own%20stakeholders%20and%20have%20made%20available%20substantive%20reports%20of%20the%20four%20rounds%20of%20negotiations%20already%20completed%2C%20and%20the%20textual%20proposals%20submitted%20to%20the%20India%20government%2C%20are%20all%20available%20on%20the%20EU%20site.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CUnfortunately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20official%20intimation%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Nayak%2C%20%E2%80%9Cwe%20are%20expected%20to%20be%20satisfied%20with%20an%20occasional%20tweet%20on%20the%20progress%20of%20the%20negotiations%20and%20brief%20press%20notes%20from%20the%20Commerce%20Ministry%20or%20MEA.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689234371000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F02%2F10140837%2Frti-cic-right-to-information.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findia-eu-fta-alber-geiger-rti-lobby-firm%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Brussels-based%20lobby%20firm%20Alber%20%26amp%3B%20Geiger%20has%20listed%20its%20assistance%20to%20the%20Indian%20government%20in%20ongoing%20India-EU%20Free%20Trade%20Agreement%20talks%2C%20under%20the%20'Wins'%20tab.%20However%2C%20three%20government%20arms%20have%20either%20denied%20or%20refused%20information%20under%20RTI%20on%20the%20hiring%20of%20the%20firm.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Findia-eu-fta-alber-geiger-rti-lobby-firm%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Go%20First%20extends%20cancellation%20of%20its%20scheduled%20flights%20till%20July%2016%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689233789000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2023-05%2F04%2Ffull%2F1683222810-491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgo-first-extends-cancellation-of-its-scheduled-flights-till-july-16-123071300391_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Go%20First%2C%20which%20is%20undergoing%20an%20insolvency%20resolution%20process%2C%20stopped%20flying%20on%20May%203%2C%20and%20since%20then%2C%20it%20has%20extended%20the%20cancellation%20of%20flights%20multiple%20times%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgo-first-extends-cancellation-of-its-scheduled-flights-till-july-16-123071300391_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgo-first-extends-cancellation-of-its-scheduled-flights-till-july-16-123071300391_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Fcompanies%2Fnews%2Fgo-first-extends-cancellation-of-its-scheduled-flights-till-july