the%20government%20will%20be%20able%20to%20grant%20a%20single%20exploration%20licence%20to%20companies%20through%20such%20auctions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CA%20single%20exploration%20licence%20will%20encourage%20more%20private%20investment%20in%20the%20sector%2C%20where%20currently%20private%20presence%20is%20limited%2C%E2%80%9D%20a%20government%20source%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Print%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fenvironment%2Flithium-reserve-jammu-kashmir-tests-india%5C%22%3EIndia%20announced%20the%20discovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20its%20very%20first%20substantial%20lithium%20deposits%2C%20amounting%20to%205.9%20million%20tonnes%2C%20in%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%E2%80%99s%20Reasi%20district.%20Experts%20had%20told%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20then%20that%20India%E2%80%99s%20lithium%20find%20is%20good%20news.%20If%20more%20assessments%20reveal%20that%20the%20lithium%20resources%20can%20indeed%20be%20tapped%20into%20and%20used%2C%20it%20will%20prove%20a%20shot%20in%20the%20arm%20for%20manufacturing%20electric%20vehicles%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20the%20development%20of%20these%20reserves%20will%20need%20to%20be%20conducted%20sustainably%20%E2%80%93%20both%20in%20terms%20of%20the%20environment%20and%20equity%20%E2%80%93%20scientists%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%2C%20the%20mines%20ministry%20had%20compiled%20the%20first%20ever%20report%20on%20identification%20of%20critical%20minerals%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1689232368000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F13124126%2Fbattery-g6f2cb070e_1280.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Funion-cabinet-clears-amendments-allowing-for-lithium-mining%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22At%20the%20moment%2C%20private%20companies%20are%20not%20allowed%20to%20mine%20these%20critical%20minerals.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A6%2C%2