3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%20%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20first%20picked%20up%20Saraam%20Chocolate%20at%20one%20of%20the%20local%20grocery%20stores%20in%20Udaipur%20where%20a%20sales%20promotion%20event%20was%20going%20on.%20I%20was%20stunned%20to%20find%20out%20that%20this%20chocolatier%20is%20just%2019.%20For%20a%2019-year-old%20to%20not%20only%20make%20amazing%20chocolate%20bars%2C%20but%20also%20%5Boversee%20the%5D%20packaging%2C%20branding%20and%20selling%20was%20quite%20a%20pleasant%20experience.%20His%20chocolates%20are%20a%20delight%20to%20eat%2C%20he%20has%20a%20great%20sense%20of%20taste%20and%20has%20been%20able%20to%20pair%20fruits%20like%20%3Cem%3Ebaer%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3Ewhich%20are%20not%20very%20common%2C%20with%20chocolate%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Abhijeet%20Karwa%2C%20one%20of%20Digvijay%E2%80%99s%20regular%20customers.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20about%20the%20importance%20of%20using%20these%20fruits%2C%20Digvijay%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20philosophy%20behind%20the%20move%20to%20using%20Indian%20native%20fruits%20is%20simple%20%E2%80%94%20to%20give%20them%20the%20importance%20they%20deserve.%20With%20my%20generation%2C%20we%20sometimes%20tend%20to%20forget%20the%20culturally%20rich%20country%20and%20its%20diverse%20flora%20and%20fauna.%20You%20know%20how%20our%20grandparents%20would%20tell%20us%20that%20they%20would%20just%20pick%20up%20fruits%20straight%20from%20trees%20and%20eat%20them%E2%80%A6we%20never%20got%20that%20chance.%20Using%20these%20fruits%20is%20a%20very%20small%20step%20but%20I%20want%20to%20introduce%20my%20generation%20to%20them.%E2%80%9D%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20chocolates%20are%20available%20to%20buy%20from%20Saraam%E2%80%99s%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.saraam.co%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewebsite%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2