ernative%20wastewater%20recycling%20systems.%20Additionally%2C%20the%20recurring%20and%20maintenance%20costs%20are%20also%20lower%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijit%20explains%20that%20greywater%20comprises%20up%20to%2075%25%20of%20daily%20water%20use.%20With%20his%20system%2C%20a%20family%20of%20five%20can%20save%20at%20least%20500%20litres%20of%20greywater%20daily.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20also%20saving%20polluted%20water%20from%20entering%20water%20bodies%20by%20recycling%20and%20reusing%20it%20at%20an%20affordable%20cost%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EEvery%20drop%20counts%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBorn%20and%20raised%20in%20Barshi%20village%20in%20the%20water-scarce%20Solapur%20district%20of%20Maharashtra%2C%20Abhijit%20would%20struggle%20for%20clean%20water.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20did%20not%20receive%20good%20monsoons.%20I%20spent%20my%20childhood%20fetching%20water%20from%20far-off%20areas.%20There%20was%20no%2024-hour%20water%20supply%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201280px)%20100vw%2C%201280px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-04-at-7.54.57-PM-1688562559.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221280%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abhijit%20has%20installed%20greywater%20systems%20in%2025%20places%20including%20residential%20complexes%2C%20schools%2C%20hostels%2C%20office%20quarters%2C%20and%20public%20toilets.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-04-at-7.54.57-PM-1688562559.jpeg%201280w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-04-at-7.54.57-PM-1688562559-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-04-at-7.54.57-PM-1688562559-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-04-at-7.54.57-PM-1688562559-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2FWhatsApp-Image-2023-07-04-at-7.54.57-PM-1688562559-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-322819%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22960%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EAbhijit%20has%20installed%20greywater%20systems%20in%2025%20places%20including%20residential%20complexes%2C%20schools%2C%20hostels%2C%20office%20quarters%2C%20and%20public%20toilets.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20he%20graduated%20from%20IIT%20Madras%2C%20the%20engineer%20went%20to%20the%20US%20for%20higher%20education%20and%20work.%20In%202012%2C%20when%20he%20came%20back%20to%20India%2C%20he%20strived%20to%20start%20his%20own%20venture.%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20that%20most%20of%20the%20engineering%20jobs%20are%20service%20and%20sales-based%2C%20not%20product%20based.%20I%20was%20not%20very%20comfortable%20pursuing%20a%20job%20in%20the%20sales%20field.%20I%20wanted%20to%20start%20my%20own%20business%20and%20the%20water%20sector%20was%20always%20on%20my%20mind%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20India%2C%20some%20areas%20are%20largely%20dependent%20on%20water%20tankers%20for%20daily%20needs%2C%20yet%20people%20do%20not%20feel%20as%20accountable%20to%20save%20water%20%E2%80%94%20a%20precious%20resource%20%E2%80%94%20as%20they%20get%20water%20by%20pressing%20a%20button%2C%20it%20is%20only%20when%20you%20face%20its%20shortage%20that%20you%20become%20vigilant%20about%20conserving%20it.%20I%20started%20figuring%20out%20ways%20to%20come%20up%20with%20recycling%20and%20reusing%20water%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20after%20a%20decade%20of%20corporate%20experience%2C%20he%20quit%20his%20well-paid%20job%20to%20start%20Jal%20Sevak%20Solutions%20in%202018.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20installed%20greywater%20systems%20in%2025%20places%20including%20residential%20complexes%2C%20individual%20homes%2C%20apartments%2C%20schools%2C%20hostels%2C%20office%20quarters%2C%20and%20public%20toilets%20across%2012%20cities%20including%20Kanpur%2C%20Hyderabad%2C%20Coimbatore%2C%20Delhi%2C%20Mumbai%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Gorakhpur.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20kitchen%20sinks%20to%20toilets%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhijit%E2%80%99s%20low-cost%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F135718%2Fgreywater-recycling-home-guide-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egreywater%20recycling%20system%20%3C%2Fa%3Eis%20a%20six-step%20process.%20Explaining%20how%20it%20works%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CFirstly%2C%20we%20collect%20greywater%20from%20showers%2C%20kitchen%20sinks%2C%20washing%20machines%2C%20and%20washbasins.%20This%20greywater%20contains%20suspended%20solids%2C%20dirt%2C%20mud%2C%20nails%2C%20dissolved%20soap%2C%20and%20a%20negligible%20percentage%20of%20bacteria.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20greywater%20is%20sent%20through%20multiple%20layers%20of%20filters%20to%20remove%20all%20suspended%20solids.%20Filters%20capture%20particles%20of%20up%20to%205%20%C2%B5m%20size%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed%20wp-block-embed-youtube%20wp-embed-aspect-16-9%20wp-has-aspect-ratio%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-embed__wrapper%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ciframe%20data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll%20data-origheight%3D%5C%22270%5C%22%20allowfullscreen%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fiyuvln5Ut0E%3Fenablejsapi%3D1%26autoplay%3D0%26cc_load_policy%3D0%26cc_lang_pref%3D%26iv_load_policy%3D3%26loop%3D0%26modestbranding%3D0%26rel%3D0%26fs%3D1%26playsinline%3D0%26autohide%3D2%26theme%3Ddark%26color%3Dred%26controls%3D1%26%5C%22%20data-no-lazy%3D%5C%221%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20player%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22480%